78  internal class MyMoveNetCommand : IMyNetworkCommand
79  {
80  private MyCharacter m_character;
81  private Vector3 m_move;
82  private Quaternion m_rotation;
83 
84  public MyMoveNetCommand(MyCharacter character, ref Vector3 move, ref Quaternion rotation)
85  {
86  m_character = character;
87  m_move = move;
88  m_rotation = rotation;
89  }
90 
91  public void Apply()
92  {
93  m_character.ApplyRotation(m_rotation);
94  m_character.MoveAndRotate(m_move, Vector2.Zero, 0);
95  m_character.MoveAndRotateInternal(m_move, Vector2.Zero, 0, Vector3.Zero);
96  }
97 
98  public bool ExecuteBeforeMoveAndRotate { get { return false; } }
99  }

101  internal class MyDeltaNetCommand : IMyNetworkCommand
102  {
103  private MyCharacter m_character;
104  private Vector3D m_delta;
105 
106  public MyDeltaNetCommand(MyCharacter character, ref Vector3D delta)
107  {
108  m_character = character;
109  m_delta = delta;
110  }
111 
112  public void Apply()
113  {
114  var old = m_character.WorldMatrix;
115  old.Translation += m_delta;
116  m_character.PositionComp.SetWorldMatrix(old, null, true);
117  }
118 
119  public bool ExecuteBeforeMoveAndRotate { get { return true; } }
120  }

499  float IMyCharacter.BaseMass { get { return this.BaseMass; } }
500  float IMyCharacter.CurrentMass { get { return this.CurrentMass; } }
501  public float BaseMass { get { return Physics.Mass; } }
502 
503  public float CurrentMass
504  {
505  get
506  {
507  float carriedMass = 0.0f;
508  if (ManipulatedEntity != null && ManipulatedEntity.Physics != null)
509  carriedMass = ManipulatedEntity.Physics.Mass;
510  if (this.GetInventory() != null)
511  {
512  return BaseMass + (float)this.GetInventory().CurrentMass + carriedMass;
513  }
514  return BaseMass + carriedMass;
515  }
516  }

812  private static string GetRealModel(string asset, ref Vector3 colorMask)
813  {
814  if (MyObjectBuilder_Character.CharacterModels.ContainsKey(asset))
815  {
816  SerializableVector3 newColorMask = MyObjectBuilder_Character.CharacterModels[asset];
817  if (newColorMask.X > -1.0f || newColorMask.Y > -1.0f || newColorMask.Z > -1.0f)
818  colorMask = newColorMask;
819  asset = DefaultModel;
820  }
821  return asset;
822  }

925  CalculateTransforms(0);
926

974  {

976  }
977

979  {
980  if (characterOb.EnabledComponents.All(x => x != componentName))
981  characterOb.EnabledComponents.Add(componentName);

992  }

995  {
996  AtmosphereDetectorComp = new MyAtmosphereDetectorComponent();

998  }
999

1001  {
1002  ReverbDetectorComp = new MyEntityReverbDetectorComponent();
1003  ReverbDetectorComp.InitComponent(this, true);//only local player will do updates
1004  }
1005 
1006  bool hasGases = Definition.SuitResourceStorage.Count > 0;
1007  var sinkData = new List<MyResourceSinkInfo>();
1008  var sourceData = new List<MyResourceSourceInfo>();
1009 
1010  if (hasGases)
1011  {
1012  OxygenComponent = new MyCharacterOxygenComponent();
1013  Components.Add(OxygenComponent);
1014  OxygenComponent.Init(characterOb);
1015  OxygenComponent.AppendSinkData(sinkData);
1016  OxygenComponent.AppendSourceData(sourceData);
1017  }
1018

1020  m_suitBattery.Init(characterOb.Battery, sinkData, sourceData);
1021 
1022  if (hasGases)
1023  {
1024  OxygenComponent.CharacterGasSink = m_suitBattery.ResourceSink;
1025  OxygenComponent.CharacterGasSource = m_suitBattery.ResourceSource;
1026  }
1027 
1028  sinkData.Clear();

1031  new MyResourceSinkInfo
1032  {
1033  ResourceTypeId = MyResourceDistributorComponent.ElectricityId,
1034  MaxRequiredInput = MyEnergyConstants.REQUIRED_INPUT_LIFE_SUPPORT + MyEnergyConstants.REQUIRED_INPUT_CHARACTER_LIGHT,
1035  RequiredInputFunc = ComputeRequiredPower
1036  });
1037 
1038  if (hasGases)
1039  {
1040  sinkData.Add(new MyResourceSinkInfo
1041  {
1042  ResourceTypeId = MyCharacterOxygenComponent.OxygenId,
1043  MaxRequiredInput = (OxygenComponent.OxygenCapacity + (!OxygenComponent.NeedsOxygenFromSuit ? Definition.OxygenConsumption : 0f)) * Definition.OxygenConsumptionMultiplier * VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEPS_PER_SECOND / 100f,
1044  RequiredInputFunc = () => (OxygenComponent.HelmetEnabled ? Definition.OxygenConsumption : 0f) * Definition.OxygenConsumptionMultiplier * VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEPS_PER_SECOND / 100f
1045  });
1046  }
1047 
1048  SinkComp.Init(
1049  MyStringHash.GetOrCompute("Utility"),
1050  sinkData);
1051  SinkComp.CurrentInputChanged += delegate
1052  {

1054  };
1055  SinkComp.TemporaryConnectedEntity = this;
1056

1058  SuitRechargeDistributor.AddSource(m_suitBattery.ResourceSource);

1063

1068  }

1077  CreateBodyCapsulesForHits(Definition.RagdollBonesMappings);
1078  else
1079  m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Clear();
1080 
1081  PlayCharacterAnimation(Definition.InitialAnimation, MyBlendOption.Immediate, MyFrameOption.JustFirstFrame, 0.0f);
1082 
1083  m_savedHealth = characterOb.Health;
1084 
1085  m_savedPlayer = new Sandbox.Game.World.MyPlayer.PlayerId(characterOb.PlayerSteamId, characterOb.PlayerSerialId);
1086 
1087  NeedsUpdate |= MyEntityUpdateEnum.BEFORE_NEXT_FRAME; // TODO: Get rid of after after the character will be initialized properly from objectBuilder
1088

1090 
1091  if (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled())
1092  {
1093  //m_localHeadTransform = new MyTransform(Vector3.Zero);

1098  CharacterGeneralDamageModifier = characterOb.CharacterGeneralDamageModifier;
1099  }

1105  private void CheckExistingStatComponent()
1106  {
1107  if (StatComp == null)
1108  {
1109  bool hasStatComponentDefinition = false;
1110  MyContainerDefinition containerDefinition = null;
1111  MyComponentContainerExtension.TryGetContainerDefinition(m_characterDefinition.Id.TypeId, m_characterDefinition.Id.SubtypeId, out containerDefinition);
1112  if (containerDefinition != null)
1113  {
1114  foreach (var componentId in containerDefinition.DefaultComponents)
1115  {
1116  if (componentId.BuilderType == typeof(MyObjectBuilder_CharacterStatComponent))
1117  {
1118  hasStatComponentDefinition = true;
1119  break;
1120  }
1121  }
1122  }
1123 
1124  string msg = "Stat component has not been created for character: " + m_characterDefinition.Id + ", container defined: " + (containerDefinition != null)
1125  + ", stat component defined: " + hasStatComponentDefinition;
1126  Debug.Fail(msg);
1127  MyLog.Default.WriteLine(msg);
1128  }
1129  }

1131  public static void GetModelAndDefinition(MyObjectBuilder_Character characterOb, out string characterModel, out MyCharacterDefinition characterDefinition, ref Vector3 colorMask)
1132  {
1133  characterModel = GetRealModel(characterOb.CharacterModel, ref colorMask);
1134  characterDefinition = null;
1135 
1136  if (!MyDefinitionManager.Static.Characters.TryGetValue(characterModel, out characterDefinition))
1137  {
1138  //System.Diagnostics.Debug.Fail("Character model " + m_characterModel + " not found!");
1139  characterDefinition = MyDefinitionManager.Static.Characters.First();
1140 
1141  characterModel = characterDefinition.Model;
1142  }

1145  private void InitInventory(MyObjectBuilder_Character characterOb)
1146  {
1147  bool inventoryAlreadyExists = this.GetInventory() != null;
1148 
1149  if (!inventoryAlreadyExists)
1150  {
1151  if (m_characterDefinition.InventoryDefinition == null)
1152  {
1153  m_characterDefinition.InventoryDefinition = new MyObjectBuilder_InventoryDefinition();
1154  }
1155 
1156  MyInventory currentInventory = new MyInventory(m_characterDefinition.InventoryDefinition, 0);
1157 
1158  // CH: This is very ugly, but it is caused by the fact that we don't have proper inventory definitions
1159  // and I didn't want to add max item count to inventory constructors
1160  currentInventory.Init(null);
1161 
1162  if (InventoryAggregate != null)
1163  {
1164  InventoryAggregate.AddComponent(currentInventory);
1165  }
1166  else
1167  {
1168  Components.Add<MyInventoryBase>(currentInventory);
1169  }
1170  currentInventory.Init(characterOb.Inventory);
1171 
1172  Debug.Assert(currentInventory.Owner == this, "Inventory ownership was not set!");
1173 
1174  // Creates the aggregate inventory
1175  MyCubeBuilder.BuildComponent.AfterCharacterCreate(this);
1176  if (MyFakes.ENABLE_MEDIEVAL_INVENTORY && InventoryAggregate != null)
1177  {
1178  var internalAggregate = InventoryAggregate.GetInventory(MyStringHash.GetOrCompute("Internal")) as MyInventoryAggregate;
1179  if (internalAggregate != null)
1180  {
1181  internalAggregate.AddComponent(currentInventory);
1182  }
1183  else
1184  {
1185  InventoryAggregate.AddComponent(currentInventory);
1186  }
1187  }
1188  }
1189  else if (MyPerGameSettings.ConstrainInventory())
1190  {
1191  MyInventory inventory = this.GetInventory();
1192  inventory.FixInventoryVolume(m_characterDefinition.InventoryDefinition.InventoryVolume);
1193  }
1194 
1195  //GR: This is a good spot for registering multiple events and calling them a lot of times... So unregister first and then register
1196  this.GetInventory().ContentsChanged -= inventory_OnContentsChanged;
1197  this.GetInventory().BeforeContentsChanged -= inventory_OnBeforeContentsChanged;
1198  this.GetInventory().BeforeRemovedFromContainer -= inventory_OnRemovedFromContainer;
1199  this.GetInventory().ContentsChanged += inventory_OnContentsChanged;
1200  this.GetInventory().BeforeContentsChanged += inventory_OnBeforeContentsChanged;
1201  this.GetInventory().BeforeRemovedFromContainer += inventory_OnRemovedFromContainer;
1202  }
1203 
1204  private void CreateBodyCapsulesForHits(Dictionary<string, MyCharacterDefinition.RagdollBoneSet> bonesMappings)
1205  {
1206  m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Clear();
1207  m_bodyCapsules = new CapsuleD[bonesMappings.Count];
1208  foreach (var boneSet in bonesMappings)
1209  {
1210  try
1211  {
1212  String[] boneNames = boneSet.Value.Bones;
1213  int ascendantBone;
1214  int descendantBone;
1215  Debug.Assert(boneNames.Length >= 2, "In ragdoll model definition of bonesets is only one bone, can not create body capsule properly! Model:" + ModelName + " BoneSet:" + boneSet.Key);
1216  var bone1 = AnimationController.FindBone(boneNames.First(), out ascendantBone);
1217  var bone2 = AnimationController.FindBone(boneNames.Last(), out descendantBone);
1218  if (bone1.Depth > bone2.Depth)
1219  {
1220  var temp = ascendantBone;
1221  ascendantBone = descendantBone;
1222  descendantBone = temp;
1223  }
1224 
1225  m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Add(new MyBoneCapsuleInfo() { Bone1 = bone1.Index, Bone2 = bone2.Index, AscendantBone = ascendantBone, DescendantBone = descendantBone, Radius = boneSet.Value.CollisionRadius });
1226  }
1227  catch (Exception e)
1228  {
1229  Debug.Fail(e.Message);
1230  }
1231  }
1232  // locating the head bone and moving as the first in the list
1233  for (int i = 0; i < m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Count; ++i)
1234  {
1235  var capsuleInfo = m_bodyCapsuleInfo[i];
1236  if (capsuleInfo.Bone1 == m_headBoneIndex)
1237  {
1238  m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Move(i, 0);
1239  break;
1240  }
1241  }
1242  }
1243 
1244  private void Toolbar_ItemChanged(MyToolbar toolbar, MyToolbar.IndexArgs index)
1245  {
1246  var item = toolbar.GetItemAtIndex(index.ItemIndex);
1247  if (item != null)
1248  {
1249  var def = item as MyToolbarItemDefinition;
1250  if (def != null)
1251  {
1252  var defId = def.Definition.Id;
1253  if (defId != null)
1254  {
1255  if (defId.TypeId != typeof(MyObjectBuilder_PhysicalGunObject))
1256  MyToolBarCollection.RequestChangeSlotItem(MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer.Id, index.ItemIndex, defId);
1257  else
1258  MyToolBarCollection.RequestChangeSlotItem(MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer.Id, index.ItemIndex, item.GetObjectBuilder());
1259  }
1260  }
1261  }
1262  else if (MySandboxGame.IsGameReady)
1263  {
1264  MyToolBarCollection.RequestClearSlot(MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer.Id, index.ItemIndex);
1265  }
1266  }

1268  private void inventory_OnRemovedFromContainer(MyEntityComponentBase component)
1269  {
1270  Debug.Assert(this.GetInventory().Entity == this, "Inventory is not longer owned by this character !");
1271  this.GetInventory().BeforeRemovedFromContainer -= inventory_OnRemovedFromContainer;
1272  this.GetInventory().ContentsChanged -= inventory_OnContentsChanged;
1273  this.GetInventory().BeforeContentsChanged -= inventory_OnBeforeContentsChanged;
1274  }
1275 
1276  private void inventory_OnContentsChanged(MyInventoryBase inventory)
1277  {
1278  if (this != MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
1279  {
1280  return;
1281  }
1282  // Switch away from the weapon if we don't have it; Cube placer is an exception
1283  if (m_currentWeapon != null && WeaponTakesBuilderFromInventory(m_currentWeapon.DefinitionId)
1284  && inventory != null && inventory is MyInventory && !(inventory as MyInventory).ContainItems(1, m_currentWeapon.PhysicalObject))
1285  SwitchToWeapon(null);
1286 
1287  // The same needs to be done with the m_leftHandItems, otherwise HandTorch
1288  if (LeftHandItem != null && !CanSwitchToWeapon(LeftHandItem.DefinitionId))
1289  {
1290  LeftHandItem.OnControlReleased();
1291  m_leftHandItem.Close();
1292  m_leftHandItem = null;
1293  }
1294  }
1295 
1296  private void inventory_OnBeforeContentsChanged(MyInventoryBase inventory)
1297  {
1298  if (this != MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
1299  {
1300  return;
1301  }
1302 
1303  if (m_currentWeapon != null && WeaponTakesBuilderFromInventory(m_currentWeapon.DefinitionId)
1304  && inventory != null && inventory is MyInventory && (inventory as MyInventory).ContainItems(1, m_currentWeapon.PhysicalObject))
1305  SaveAmmoToWeapon();//because it may be dropped few electrons later
1306  }
1307 
1308  private void RigidBody_ContactPointCallback(ref HkContactPointEvent value)
1309  {
1310  if (IsDead || Sync.IsServer == false)
1311  return;
1312 
1313  if (Physics.CharacterProxy == null)
1314  return;
1315 
1316  if (!MySession.Static.Ready)
1317  return;
1318 
1319  if (value.Base.BodyA == null || value.Base.BodyB == null)
1320  return;
1321 
1322  if (value.Base.BodyA.UserObject == null || value.Base.BodyB.UserObject == null)
1323  return;
1324 
1325  if (value.Base.BodyA.HasProperty(HkCharacterRigidBody.MANIPULATED_OBJECT) || value.Base.BodyB.HasProperty(HkCharacterRigidBody.MANIPULATED_OBJECT))
1326  return;
1327 
1328  //MyCharacter charA = null;//((MyPhysicsBody)value.Base.BodyA.UserObject).Entity as MyCharacter;
1329  //MyCharacter charB = null;//((MyPhysicsBody)value.Base.BodyB.UserObject).Entity as MyCharacter;
1330 
1331  //if (charA != null && charA.AIMode)
1332  // return;
1333 
1334  //if (charB != null && charB.AIMode)
1335  // return;
1336 
1337  Render.TrySpawnWalkingParticles(ref value);
1338 
1339  // DAMAGE COMPUTATION TO THE CHARACTER
1340  // GET THE OTHER COLLIDING BODY AND COMPUTE DAMAGE BASED ON BODIES MASS AND VELOCITIES
1341  if (MyPerGameSettings.EnableCharacterCollisionDamage && !MyFakes.NEW_CHARACTER_DAMAGE)
1342  {
1343  CalculateDamageAfterCollision(ref value);
1344  }
1346  else
1347  {
1348  float impact = 0;
1349 
1350  if (MyFakes.NEW_CHARACTER_DAMAGE)
1351  {
1352  var normal = value.ContactPoint.Normal;
1353  MyEntity other = value.GetPhysicsBody(0).Entity as MyEntity;
1354 
1355  HkRigidBody otherRb = value.Base.BodyA;
1356  if (other == this)
1357  {
1358  other = value.GetPhysicsBody(1).Entity as MyEntity;
1359  otherRb = value.Base.BodyB;
1360  normal = -normal;
1361  }
1362 
1363  var otherChar = (other as MyCharacter);
1364  if (otherChar != null)
1365  {
1366  if (otherChar.IsDead)
1367  {
1368  if (otherChar.Physics.Ragdoll != null && otherChar.Physics.Ragdoll.GetRootRigidBody().HasProperty(HkCharacterRigidBody.MANIPULATED_OBJECT))
1369  return;
1370  }
1371  else
1372  {
1373  if (Physics.CharacterProxy.Supported && otherChar.Physics.CharacterProxy.Supported)
1374  return;
1375  }
1376  }
1377 
1378  if (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) < 3)
1379  {
1380  return;
1381  }
1382 
1383  Vector3 velocity1 = Physics.LinearVelocity;
1384 
1385  Vector3 difference = velocity1 - m_previousLinearVelocity;
1386 
1387  float lenght = difference.Length();
1388 
1389  if (lenght > 10)
1390  {
1391  //strange angle / magnitude force mismatch
1392  return;
1393  }
1394 
1395  Vector3 velocity2 = otherRb.GetVelocityAtPoint(value.ContactPoint.Position);
1396 
1397  float velocity = velocity1.Length();
1398  float speed1 = Math.Max(velocity - (MyFakes.ENABLE_CUSTOM_CHARACTER_IMPACT ? 12.6f : 17.0f), 0);//treshold for falling dmg
1399  float speed2 = velocity2.Length() - 2.0f;
1400 
1401  Vector3 dir1 = speed1 > 0 ? Vector3.Normalize(velocity1) : Vector3.Zero;
1402  Vector3 dir2 = speed2 > 0 ? Vector3.Normalize(velocity2) : Vector3.Zero;
1403 
1404  float dot1withNormal = speed1 > 0 ? Vector3.Dot(dir1, normal) : 0;
1405  float dot2withNormal = speed2 > 0 ? -Vector3.Dot(dir2, normal) : 0;
1406 
1407  speed1 *= dot1withNormal;
1408  speed2 *= dot2withNormal;
1409 
1410  float vel = Math.Min(speed1 + speed2, Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) - 17.0f);
1411  if (vel >= -8f && m_canPlayImpact <= 0f)//impact sound
1412  {
1413  m_canPlayImpact = 0.3f;
1414  HkContactPointEvent hkContactPointEvent = value;
1415  Func<bool> canHear = () =>
1416  {
1417  if (MySession.Static.ControlledEntity != null)
1418  {
1419  var entity = MySession.Static.ControlledEntity.Entity.GetTopMostParent();
1420  return (entity == hkContactPointEvent.GetPhysicsBody(0).Entity || entity == hkContactPointEvent.GetPhysicsBody(1).Entity);
1421  }
1422  return false;
1423  };
1424  var bodyB = value.Base.BodyB.GetBody();
1425  var worldPos = Physics.ClusterToWorld(value.ContactPoint.Position);
1426  var materialB = bodyB.GetMaterialAt(worldPos - value.ContactPoint.Normal * 0.1f);
1427  float volume = (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) < 15f) ? (0.5f + Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) / 30f) : 1f;
1428  MyAudioComponent.PlayContactSound(Entity.EntityId, m_stringIdHit, worldPos, m_stringHashCharacter, materialB, volume, canHear);
1429  }
1430  if (vel < 0)
1431  return;
1432 
1433  float mass1 = MyDestructionHelper.MassFromHavok(Physics.Mass * this.m_massChangeForCollisions);
1434  float mass2 = MyDestructionHelper.MassFromHavok(otherRb.Mass * other.m_massChangeForCollisions);
1435 
1436  float impact1 = (speed1 * speed1 * mass1) * 0.5f;
1437  float impact2 = (speed2 * speed2 * mass2) * 0.5f;
1438 
1439  float mass;
1440  if (mass1 > mass2 && !otherRb.IsFixedOrKeyframed)
1441  {
1442  mass = mass2;
1443  //impact = impact2;
1444  }
1445  else
1446  {
1447  mass = MyDestructionHelper.MassToHavok(70);// Physics.Mass;
1448  if (Physics.CharacterProxy.Supported && !otherRb.IsFixedOrKeyframed)
1449  mass += Math.Abs(Vector3.Dot(Vector3.Normalize(velocity2), Physics.CharacterProxy.SupportNormal)) * mass2 / 10;
1450  }
1451  mass = MyDestructionHelper.MassFromHavok(mass);
1452 
1453  impact = (mass * vel * vel) / 2;
1454  if (speed2 > 2) //dont reduce pure fall damage
1455  impact -= 400;
1456  impact /= 10; //scaling damage
1457  if (impact < 1)
1458  return;
1459  }
1460 
1461  //int bodyId = value.Base.BodyA == Physics.CharacterProxy.GetRigidBody() ? 1 : 0;
1462  // Ca
1463  //uint shapeKey = value.GetShapeKey(bodyId);
1464  //if (shapeKey != uint.MaxValue)
1465  {
1466  //m_shapeContactPoints.Add(shapeKey);
1467 
1468  //MyTrace.Send(TraceWindow.Default, "Velocity: " + value.SeparatingVelocity.ToString());
1469  //if (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) > 0)
1470  //{
1471  //}
1472 
1473  //2 large blocks (14.3m/s)
1474  //3 large blocks (17.0m/s)
1475  //5 large blocks (22.3m/s)
1476  //6 large blocks (24.2m/s)
1477  float damageImpact = (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) - 17.0f) * 14.0f;
1478 
1479  if (MyFakes.ENABLE_CUSTOM_CHARACTER_IMPACT)
1480  {
1481  // 1.5 ~ start damage (12.6m/s)
1482  // 3 blocks - dead (17.0)
1483  damageImpact = (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) - 12.6f) * 25f;
1484  }
1485  if (MyFakes.NEW_CHARACTER_DAMAGE)
1486  damageImpact = impact;
1487  if (damageImpact > 0)
1488  {
1489  if (Sync.IsServer)
1490  {
1491  IMyEntity other = value.GetPhysicsBody(0).Entity;
1492  if (other == this)
1493  other = value.GetPhysicsBody(1).Entity;
1494 
1495  DoDamage(damageImpact, MyDamageType.Environment, true, other != null ? other.EntityId : 0);
1496  }
1497  }
1498  }
1499  }
1500  }
1501 
1502  private void CalculateDamageAfterCollision(ref HkContactPointEvent value)
1503  {
1504  // Are bodies moving one to another? if not we do not apply damage
1505  if (value.SeparatingVelocity < 0)
1506  {
1507  if (!Sync.IsServer) return;
1508 
1509  DamageImpactEnum damageImpact = DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1510 
1511  // Get the colliding object and skip collisions between characters
1512  HkRigidBody collidingBody;
1513  int collidingBodyIdx = 0;
1514  if (value.Base.BodyA == Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody())
1515  {
1516  collidingBody = value.Base.BodyB;
1517  collidingBodyIdx = 1;
1518  }
1519  else
1520  collidingBody = value.Base.BodyA;
1521  MyEntity collidingEntity = value.GetPhysicsBody(collidingBodyIdx).Entity as MyEntity;
1522  if (collidingEntity == null || collidingEntity is MyCharacter) return;
1523 
1524  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
1525  {
1526  MatrixD worldMatrix = collidingEntity.Physics.GetWorldMatrix();
1527  int index = 0;
1528  MyPhysicsDebugDraw.DrawCollisionShape(collidingBody.GetShape(), worldMatrix, 1, ref index, "hit");
1529  }
1530 
1531  damageImpact = GetDamageFromFall(collidingBody, collidingEntity, ref value);
1532 
1533  if (damageImpact != DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage) ApplyDamage(damageImpact, MyDamageType.Fall);
1534 
1535  damageImpact = GetDamageFromHit(collidingBody, collidingEntity, ref value);
1536 
1537  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
1538  {
1539  if (damageImpact != DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage)
1540  {
1541  MatrixD worldMatrix = collidingEntity.Physics.GetWorldMatrix();
1542  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawSphere(worldMatrix.Translation, collidingBody.Mass, Color.Red, 1, false);
1543  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawText3D(worldMatrix.Translation, "MASS: " + collidingBody.Mass, Color.Red, 1, false);
1544  }
1545  }
1546 
1547  if (damageImpact != DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage) ApplyDamage(damageImpact, MyDamageType.Environment);
1548 
1549  damageImpact = GetDamageFromSqueeze(collidingBody, collidingEntity, ref value);
1550 
1551  if (damageImpact != DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage) ApplyDamage(damageImpact, MyDamageType.Squeez);
1552  }
1553  }
1554 
1555  private DamageImpactEnum GetDamageFromSqueeze(HkRigidBody collidingBody, MyEntity collidingEntity, ref HkContactPointEvent value)
1556  {
1557  if (collidingBody.IsFixed || collidingBody.Mass < MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSqueezeMinMass) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1558 
1559  if (value.ContactProperties.IsNew) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1560 
1561  // the object has to be moving towards the character even slowly and that also the character is not moving away from it
1562  Vector3 direction = Physics.CharacterProxy.Position - collidingBody.Position;
1563  direction.Normalize();
1564  var gravity = m_gravity;
1565  gravity.Normalize();
1566 
1567  float resultToPlayer = Vector3.Dot(direction, gravity);
1568 
1569  if (resultToPlayer < 0.5f) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1570 
1571  if (m_squeezeDamageTimer > 0)
1572  {
1573  m_squeezeDamageTimer -= VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
1574  return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1575  }
1576  m_squeezeDamageTimer = MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSqueezeDamageDelay;
1577 
1578  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
1579  {
1580  MatrixD worldMatrix = collidingEntity.Physics.GetWorldMatrix();
1581  int index = 2;
1582  MyPhysicsDebugDraw.DrawCollisionShape(collidingBody.GetShape(), worldMatrix, 1, ref index);
1583  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawText3D(worldMatrix.Translation, "SQUEEZE, MASS:" + collidingBody.Mass, Color.Yellow, 2, false);
1584  }
1585 
1586  if (collidingBody.Mass > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSqueezeDeadlyDamageMass) return DamageImpactEnum.DeadlyDamage;
1587 
1588  if (collidingBody.Mass > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSqueezeCriticalDamageMass) return DamageImpactEnum.CriticalDamage;
1589 
1590  if (collidingBody.Mass > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSqueezeMediumDamageMass) return DamageImpactEnum.MediumDamage;
1591 
1592  return DamageImpactEnum.SmallDamage;
1593  }
1594 
1595  private DamageImpactEnum GetDamageFromHit(HkRigidBody collidingBody, MyEntity collidingEntity, ref HkContactPointEvent value)
1596  {
1597  if (collidingBody.LinearVelocity.Length() < MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectMinVelocity) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1598 
1599  if (collidingEntity == ManipulatedEntity) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1600 
1601  if (collidingBody.HasProperty(HkCharacterRigidBody.MANIPULATED_OBJECT)) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1602 
1603  var mass = (MyPerGameSettings.Destruction ? MyDestructionHelper.MassFromHavok(collidingBody.Mass) : collidingBody.Mass);
1604  if (mass < MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectMinMass) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1605 
1606  // Get the objects energies to calculate the damage - must be higher above treshold
1607  float objectEnergy = Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity) * mass;
1608 
1609  if (objectEnergy > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectDeadlyEnergy) return DamageImpactEnum.DeadlyDamage;
1610  if (objectEnergy > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectCriticalEnergy) return DamageImpactEnum.CriticalDamage;
1611  if (objectEnergy > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectMediumEnergy) return DamageImpactEnum.MediumDamage;
1612  if (objectEnergy > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageHitObjectSmallEnergy) return DamageImpactEnum.SmallDamage;
1613 
1614  return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1615  }
1616 
1617  private void ApplyDamage(DamageImpactEnum damageImpact, MyStringHash myDamageType)
1618  {
1619  if (!Sync.IsServer) return;
1620 
1621  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
1622  {
1623  if (damageImpact != DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage)
1624  {
1625  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawText2D(new Vector2(100, 100), "DAMAGE! TYPE: " + myDamageType.ToString() + " IMPACT: " + damageImpact.ToString(), Color.Red, 1);
1626  }
1627  }
1628 
1629  switch (damageImpact)
1630  {
1631  case DamageImpactEnum.SmallDamage:
1632  DoDamage(MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSmallDamage, myDamageType, true);
1633  break;
1634 
1635  case DamageImpactEnum.MediumDamage:
1636  DoDamage(MyPerGameSettings.CharacterMediumDamage, myDamageType, true);
1637  break;
1638 
1639  case DamageImpactEnum.CriticalDamage:
1640  DoDamage(MyPerGameSettings.CharacterCriticalDamage, myDamageType, true);
1641  break;
1642 
1643  case DamageImpactEnum.DeadlyDamage:
1644  DoDamage(MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDeadlyDamage, myDamageType, true);
1645  break;
1646 
1647  case DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage:
1648  default:
1649  break;
1650  }
1651  }
1652 
1653  private DamageImpactEnum GetDamageFromFall(HkRigidBody collidingBody, MyEntity collidingEntity, ref HkContactPointEvent value)
1654  {
1655  //if (m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Falling || m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1656  //if (!collidingBody.IsFixed && collidingBody.Mass < Physics.Mass * 50) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1657 
1658  float dotProd = Vector3.Dot(value.ContactPoint.Normal, Vector3.Normalize(Physics.HavokWorld.Gravity));
1659 
1660  bool falledOnEntity = dotProd <= 0.0f;
1661 
1662  if (!falledOnEntity) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1663 
1664  if (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity * dotProd) < MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageMinVelocity) return DamageImpactEnum.NoDamage;
1665 
1666  if (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity * dotProd) > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageDeadlyDamageVelocity) return DamageImpactEnum.DeadlyDamage;
1667 
1668  if (Math.Abs(value.SeparatingVelocity * dotProd) > MyPerGameSettings.CharacterDamageMediumDamageVelocity) return DamageImpactEnum.MediumDamage;
1669 
1670  return DamageImpactEnum.SmallDamage;
1671  }

1673  private void InitWeapon(MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase weapon)
1674  {
1675  if (weapon == null)
1676  return;
1677  if ((m_rightHandItemBone == -1 || weapon != null) && m_currentWeapon != null)
1678  {
1679  // First, dispose of the old weapon
1680  DisposeWeapon();
1681  }
1682  var physicalItemDefinition = MyDefinitionManager.Static.GetPhysicalItemForHandItem(weapon.GetId());
1683  Debug.Assert(this.GetInventory() != null);
1684  bool canEquipWeapon = physicalItemDefinition != null && (!MySession.Static.SurvivalMode || (this.GetInventory().GetItemAmount(physicalItemDefinition.Id) > 0));
1685 
1686  if (m_rightHandItemBone != -1 && canEquipWeapon)
1687  {
1688  m_currentWeapon = CreateGun(weapon);
1689  }
1690  }

1694  if (m_rightHandItemBone == -1 && m_currentWeapon != null)
1695  {
1696  DisposeWeapon();
1697  }

1700  private void DisposeWeapon()
1701  {
1702  var weaponEntity = m_currentWeapon as MyEntity;
1703  Debug.Assert(weaponEntity != null);
1704  if (weaponEntity != null)
1705  {
1706  weaponEntity.EntityId = 0;
1707  weaponEntity.Close();
1708  m_currentWeapon = null;
1709  }
1710  }

1725  objectBuilder.Inventory = null;
1726  }

1736 
1737  objectBuilder.Health = null;
1738

1770  JetpackComp.GetObjectBuilder(objectBuilder);
1771

1773  OxygenComponent.GetObjectBuilder(objectBuilder);
1774  }

1777  objectBuilder.PlayerSteamId = m_controlInfo.Value.SteamId;
1778

1822  private bool m_wasInFirstPerson = false;
1823  private bool m_isInFirstPerson = false;
1824 
1825  public override void UpdateBeforeSimulation()
1826  {
1827  base.UpdateBeforeSimulation();
1828 
1829  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(MySession.Static != null);
1830 
1831  if (MySession.Static == null)
1832  return;
1833 
1834  // Persist current movement flags before UpdateAfterSimulation()
1835  // to safely send the client state at a later stage
1836  m_previousMovementFlags = m_movementFlags;
1837 
1838  m_previousNetworkMovementState = GetCurrentMovementState();
1839 
1840  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.GetRenderProfiler().StartProfilingBlock("Update zero movement");
1841  UpdateZeroMovement();
1842  VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.GetRenderProfiler().EndProfilingBlock();
1843 
1844  if (m_cachedCommands != null)
1845  {
1846  if (IsUsing != null)
1847  {
1848  m_cachedCommands.Clear();
1849  }
1850 
1851  foreach (var command in m_cachedCommands)
1852  {
1853  if (command.ExecuteBeforeMoveAndRotate)
1854  {
1855  command.Apply();
1856  }
1857  }
1858  }
1859 
1860  if (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled() || (IsUsing == null && (m_cachedCommands != null && m_cachedCommands.Count == 0)))
1861  {
1862  MoveAndRotateInternal(MoveIndicator, RotationIndicator, RollIndicator, RotationCenterIndicator);
1863  }
1864 
1865  if (m_cachedCommands != null)
1866  {
1867  if (IsUsing != null || IsDead)
1868  {
1869  m_cachedCommands.Clear();
1870  }
1871 
1872  foreach (var command in m_cachedCommands)
1873  {
1874  if (command.ExecuteBeforeMoveAndRotate == false)
1875  {
1876  command.Apply();
1877  }
1878  }
1879  m_cachedCommands.Clear();
1880  }
1881 
1882  m_moveAndRotateCalled = false;
1883  m_actualUpdateFrame++;
1884 
1885  m_isInFirstPerson = (MySession.Static.CameraController == this) && IsInFirstPersonView;
1886 
1887  if (m_wasInFirstPerson != m_isInFirstPerson && m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sitting)
1888  {
1889  MySector.MainCamera.Zoom.ApplyToFov = m_isInFirstPerson;
1890 
1891  if (!ForceFirstPersonCamera)
1892  {
1893  UpdateNearFlag();
1894  }
1895  }
1896 
1897  m_wasInFirstPerson = m_isInFirstPerson;
1898 
1899  UpdateLightPower();
1900 
1901  SoundComp.FindAndPlayStateSound();
1902  SoundComp.UpdateWindSounds();
1903 
1904  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
1905  if (jetpack != null && (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled() || Sync.IsServer))
1906  jetpack.UpdateBeforeSimulation();
1907 
1908  if (!IsDead && m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sitting &&
1909  !MySandboxGame.IsPaused && //this update is called even in pause (jetpack, model update)
1910  Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
1911  {
1912  Vector3 linearVelocity = Physics.LinearVelocity;
1913  Vector3 angularVelocity = Physics.AngularVelocity;
1914  if (!JetpackRunning)
1915  Physics.CharacterProxy.StepSimulation(VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS);
1916  else
1917  {
1918  Physics.CharacterProxy.UpdateSupport(VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS);
1919  //<ib.jetpack> SE-1247: Call ing MyPhysicsBody.LinearVelocity += resets to all rigid bodies in ragdoll linear velocity same as character linear velocity
1920  //Physics.LinearVelocity += Physics.Gravity * VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS; // why to add gravity as linear velocity in jetpack mode ???
1921  Physics.CharacterProxy.ApplyGravity(Physics.Gravity);
1922 
1923  }
1924 
1925  if (!Sync.IsServer && Sandbox.Engine.Utils.MyFakes.MULTIPLAYER_CLIENT_PHYSICS && !ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled())
1926  {
1927  // revert velocities for not controlled characters (synced over network), step simulation is in place just to update values like ground normal
1928  Physics.LinearVelocity = linearVelocity;
1929  Physics.AngularVelocity = angularVelocity;
1930  }
1931  }
1932

2305  private void UpdateFallAndSpine()
2306  {
2307  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
2308  if (jetpack != null)
2309  jetpack.UpdateFall();
2310 
2311  if (m_isFalling)
2312  {
2313  if (!JetpackRunning)
2314  {
2315  m_currentFallingTime += VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2316  if (m_currentFallingTime > FALL_TIME && !m_isFallingAnimationPlayed)
2317  {
2318  SwitchAnimation(MyCharacterMovementEnum.Falling, false);
2319  m_isFallingAnimationPlayed = true;
2320  }
2321  }
2322  }
2323 
2324  if ((!JetpackRunning ||
2325  (jetpack.Running && (IsLocalHeadAnimationInProgress() || Definition.VerticalPositionFlyingOnly))) &&
2326  !IsDead && !IsSitting)
2327  {
2328  float spineRotation = MathHelper.Clamp(-m_headLocalXAngle, -45, MAX_HEAD_LOCAL_X_ANGLE);
2329 
2330  float bendMultiplier = IsInFirstPersonView
2331  ? m_characterDefinition.BendMultiplier1st
2332  : m_characterDefinition.BendMultiplier3rd;
2333  var usedSpineRotation = Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Backward,
2334  MathHelper.ToRadians(bendMultiplier * spineRotation));
2335 
2336  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
2337  {
2338  float leaningValue = m_characterDefinition.BendMultiplier3rd*spineRotation;
2339  if (MySession.Static.LocalCharacter == this &&
2340  (!MyInput.Static.IsGameControlPressed(Sandbox.Game.MyControlsSpace.LOOKAROUND) || IsInFirstPersonView || ForceFirstPersonCamera || CurrentWeapon != null))
2341  {
2342  m_animLeaning = leaningValue;
2343  }
2344  }
2345  else
2346  {
2347  Quaternion clientsSpineRotation = Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Backward,
2348  MathHelper.ToRadians(m_characterDefinition.BendMultiplier3rd * spineRotation));
2349  SetSpineAdditionalRotation(usedSpineRotation, clientsSpineRotation);
2350  }
2351  }
2352  else
2353  {
2354  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
2355  {
2356  AnimationController.Variables.SetValue(MyAnimationVariableStorageHints.StrIdLean, 0);
2357  }
2358  else
2359  {
2360  SetSpineAdditionalRotation(Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Backward, 0),
2361  Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Backward, 0));
2362  }
2363  }
2364 
2365  if (m_currentWeapon == null && !IsDead && !JetpackRunning && !IsSitting)
2366  {
2367  if (m_headLocalXAngle < -11)
2368  {
2369  // THIS CAUSES CHARACTER HAND GLITCH WITH NEW MODEL
2370  //SetHandAdditionalRotation(Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Forward, MathHelper.ToRadians(0)));
2371  //SetUpperHandAdditionalRotation(Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Normalize(Vector3.Down + Vector3.Right - 0.4f * Vector3.Forward), -MathHelper.ToRadians(((m_headLocalXAngle + 11) * 0.8f))));
2372  }
2373  if (m_headLocalXAngle > -11)
2374  {
2375  //SetHandAdditionalRotation(Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Forward, MathHelper.ToRadians(0)));
2376  //SetUpperHandAdditionalRotation(Quaternion.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Forward, MathHelper.ToRadians(0)));
2377  }
2378  }
2379  else

2429 
2430  private void UpdatePhysicalMovement()
2431  {
2432  if (!MySandboxGame.IsGameReady || Physics == null || !Physics.Enabled || !MySession.Static.Ready || Physics.HavokWorld == null)
2433  return;
2434 
2435  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
2436  bool jetpackActive = !(jetpack == null || !jetpack.UpdatePhysicalMovement()); //Solve Y orientation and gravity only in non flying mode
2437 
2438  m_gravity = MyGravityProviderSystem.CalculateTotalGravityInPoint(PositionComp.WorldAABB.Center) + Physics.HavokWorld.Gravity;
2439 
2440  if ((!jetpackActive || Definition.VerticalPositionFlyingOnly || IsMagneticBootsEnabled) && !IsDead && Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
2441  {
2442  if (!Physics.CharacterProxy.Up.IsValid())
2443  {
2444  Debug.Fail("Character Proxy Up vector is invalid! Can not to solve gravity influence on character. Character type: " + this.GetType().ToString());
2445  Physics.CharacterProxy.Up = WorldMatrix.Up;
2446  }
2447 
2448  if (!Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward.IsValid())
2449  {
2450  Debug.Fail("Character Proxy Forward vector is invalid! Can not to solve gravity influence on character. Character type: " + this.GetType().ToString());
2451  Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward = WorldMatrix.Forward;
2452  }
2453 
2454  Vector3 characterUp = Physics.CharacterProxy.Up;
2455  Vector3 characterForward = Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward;
2456 
2457  if (!jetpackActive)
2458  Physics.CharacterProxy.Gravity = m_gravity * MyPerGameSettings.CharacterGravityMultiplier;
2459  else
2460  Physics.CharacterProxy.Gravity = Vector3.Zero;
2461 
2462  // If there is valid non-zero gravity
2463  if ((m_gravity.LengthSquared() > 0.1f) && (characterUp != Vector3.Zero) && m_gravity.IsValid())
2464  {
2465  UpdateStandup(ref m_gravity, ref characterUp, ref characterForward);
2466  if (jetpack != null)
2467  jetpack.CurrentAutoEnableDelay = 0;
2468  }
2469  // Zero-G
2470  else
2471  {
2472  if (IsMagneticBootsEnabled)
2473  {
2474  Vector3 normal = -Physics.CharacterProxy.SupportNormal;
2475  UpdateStandup(ref normal, ref characterUp, ref characterForward);
2476  }
2477 
2478  if (jetpack != null && jetpack.CurrentAutoEnableDelay != -1)
2479  jetpack.CurrentAutoEnableDelay += VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2480  }
2481 
2482  Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward = characterForward;
2483  Physics.CharacterProxy.Up = characterUp;
2484  }
2485  else if (IsDead)
2486  {
2487  if (Physics == null) Debugger.Break();
2488 
2489  if (Physics.HasRigidBody && Physics.RigidBody.IsActive)
2490  {
2491  Physics.RigidBody.Gravity = m_gravity;
2492  }
2493  }
2494 
2495  MatrixD worldMatrix = Physics.GetWorldMatrix();
2496  bool serverOverride = !MyFakes.MULTIPLAYER_SIMULATE_CHARACTER_CLIENT && Physics.ServerWorldMatrix.HasValue;
2497  if (serverOverride)
2498  {
2499  if (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled())
2500  worldMatrix.Translation = Physics.ServerWorldMatrix.Value.Translation;
2501  else
2502  worldMatrix = Physics.ServerWorldMatrix.Value;
2503  }
2504 
2505  //Include foot error
2506  if (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing)
2507  {
2508  m_cummulativeVerticalFootError += m_verticalFootError * 0.2f;
2509  m_cummulativeVerticalFootError = MathHelper.Clamp(m_cummulativeVerticalFootError, -0.75f, 0.75f);
2510  }
2511  else
2512  m_cummulativeVerticalFootError = 0;
2513 
2514  worldMatrix.Translation = worldMatrix.Translation + worldMatrix.Up * m_cummulativeVerticalFootError;
2515 
2516  if (Vector3D.DistanceSquared(WorldMatrix.Translation, worldMatrix.Translation) > 0.00001f ||
2517  Vector3D.DistanceSquared(WorldMatrix.Forward, worldMatrix.Forward) > 0.00001f ||
2518  Vector3D.DistanceSquared(WorldMatrix.Up, worldMatrix.Up) > 0.00001f ||
2519  serverOverride)
2520  {
2521  PositionComp.SetWorldMatrix(worldMatrix, serverOverride ? null : Physics);
2522  Physics.ServerWorldMatrix = null;
2523  }
2524 
2525  if (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled())
2526  {
2527  Physics.UpdateAccelerations();
2528  }
2529  else if (!ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled() && Sync.IsServer)
2530  {
2531  Physics.UpdateAccelerations();
2532  } //otherwise OnPositionUpdate message it is updated
2533  }
2534 
2535  private void UpdateStandup(ref Vector3 gravity, ref Vector3 chUp, ref Vector3 chForward)
2536  {
2537  Vector3 minusGravity = -Vector3.Normalize(gravity);
2538  Vector3 testUp = minusGravity;
2539  if (Physics != null && Physics.CharacterProxy != null && Physics.CharacterProxy.Supported)
2540  {
2541  Vector3 supportNormal = Physics.CharacterProxy.SupportNormal;
2542  if (Definition.RotationToSupport == MyEnumCharacterRotationToSupport.OneAxis)
2543  {
2544  float cosAngleMinusGravityToNormal = minusGravity.Dot(ref supportNormal);
2545  if (!MyUtils.IsZero(cosAngleMinusGravityToNormal - 1) &&
2546  !MyUtils.IsZero(cosAngleMinusGravityToNormal + 1))
2547  {
2548  Vector3 poleVec = minusGravity.Cross(supportNormal);
2549  poleVec.Normalize();
2550  testUp = Vector3.Lerp(supportNormal, minusGravity, Math.Abs(poleVec.Dot(WorldMatrix.Forward)));
2551  }
2552  }
2553  else if (Definition.RotationToSupport == MyEnumCharacterRotationToSupport.Full)
2554  {
2555  testUp = supportNormal;
2556  }
2557  }
2558 
2559  var dotProd = Vector3.Dot(chUp, testUp);
2560  var lenProd = chUp.Length() * testUp.Length();
2561  var divOperation = dotProd / lenProd;
2562 
2563  // check-up proper division result and for NaN
2564  if (float.IsNaN(divOperation) || float.IsNegativeInfinity(divOperation) || float.IsPositiveInfinity(divOperation)) divOperation = 1;
2565  divOperation = MathHelper.Clamp(divOperation, -1.0f, 1.0f);
2566 
2567  const float standUpSpeedAnglePerFrame = 0.04f;
2568 
2569  if (!MyUtils.IsZero(divOperation - 1, 0.00001f))
2570  {
2571  float angle = 0;
2572  //if direct opposite
2573  if (MyUtils.IsZero(divOperation + 1, 0.00001f))
2574  angle = 0.1f;
2575  else
2576  angle = (float)(Math.Acos(divOperation));
2577 
2578  angle = System.Math.Min(Math.Abs(angle), standUpSpeedAnglePerFrame) * Math.Sign(angle);
2579 
2580  Vector3 normal = Vector3.Cross(chUp, testUp);
2581 
2582  if (normal.LengthSquared() > 0)
2583  {
2584  normal = Vector3.Normalize(normal);
2585  chUp = Vector3.TransformNormal(chUp, Matrix.CreateFromAxisAngle(normal, angle));
2586  chForward = Vector3.TransformNormal(chForward, Matrix.CreateFromAxisAngle(normal, angle));
2587  }
2588  }
2589  }
2590 
2591  private void UpdateShake()
2592  {
2593  if (MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer == null)
2594  return;
2595 
2596  if (this == MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer.Identity.Character)
2597  {
2598  UpdateHudCharacterInfo();
2599 
2600  if (
2601  (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing) ||
2602  (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Crouching) ||
2603  (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Flying))
2604  m_currentHeadAnimationCounter += VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2605  else
2606  m_currentHeadAnimationCounter = 0;
2607 
2608  if (m_currentLocalHeadAnimation >= 0)
2609  {
2610  m_currentLocalHeadAnimation += VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2611 
2612  float ratio = m_currentLocalHeadAnimation / m_localHeadAnimationLength;
2613 
2614  if (m_currentLocalHeadAnimation > m_localHeadAnimationLength)
2615  {
2616  m_currentLocalHeadAnimation = -1;
2617  ratio = 1;
2618  }
2619 
2620  if (m_localHeadAnimationX.HasValue)
2621  SetHeadLocalXAngle(MathHelper.Lerp(m_localHeadAnimationX.Value.X, m_localHeadAnimationX.Value.Y, ratio));
2622  if (m_localHeadAnimationY.HasValue)
2623  SetHeadLocalYAngle(MathHelper.Lerp(m_localHeadAnimationY.Value.X, m_localHeadAnimationY.Value.Y, ratio));
2624  }
2625  }

2693  {

2695  //Line line = new Line(MySector.MainCamera.Position, MySector.MainCamera.Position + MySector.MainCamera.ForwardVector * 1000);

2700  return intersection.Value.IntersectionPointInWorldSpace;
2701  }
2702  else

2713  private Vector3D GetAimedPointFromCamera()
2714  {

2716  ? (WeaponPosition.LogicalPositionWorld + MySector.MainCamera.ForwardVector * 25000)
2717  : (MySector.MainCamera.Position + MySector.MainCamera.ForwardVector * 25000);
2718 
2719  if (MySession.Static.ControlledEntity == this)
2720  {
2721  LineD line = new LineD(MySector.MainCamera.Position, MySector.MainCamera.Position + MySector.MainCamera.ForwardVector * 100);
2722  var intersection = MyEntities.GetIntersectionWithLine(ref line, this, (MyEntity)m_currentWeapon);
2723  if (intersection.HasValue && intersection.Value.Entity != null)
2724  {
2725  endPoint = intersection.Value.IntersectionPointInWorldSpace;
2726  }
2727  }
2728 
2729 
2730  //VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawLine3D(WeaponPosition.LogicalPositionWorld, endPoint, Color.Red, Color.Red, false);
2731  //VRageRender.MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawSphere(endPoint, 0.1f, Color.Red, 1, true);
2732 
2733  // There doesn't seem to be any difference between doing the raycast and just
2734  // returning the end point. However, 25km raycast causes distant voxel maps to
2735  // generate geometry along the ray path, unless it is already cached (which it usually isn't),
2736  // and that can take very long time.
2737  return endPoint;

2825  internal void MoveAndRotateInternal(Vector3 moveIndicator, Vector2 rotationIndicator, float roll, Vector3 rotationCenter)
2826  {
2827  if (Physics == null)
2828  return;
2829 
2830  if (DebugMode)
2831  return;
2832 
2833  //Died character
2834  if (Physics.CharacterProxy == null)
2835  {
2836  moveIndicator = Vector3.Zero;
2837  rotationIndicator = Vector2.Zero;
2838  roll = 0;
2839  }
2840 
2841  bool sprint = moveIndicator.Z != 0 && WantsSprint;
2842  bool walk = WantsWalk;
2843  bool jump = WantsJump;
2844  bool canMove = !JetpackRunning && !((m_currentCharacterState == HkCharacterStateType.HK_CHARACTER_IN_AIR || (int)m_currentCharacterState == MyCharacter.HK_CHARACTER_FLYING) && (m_currentJumpTime <= 0)) && (m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died);
2845  bool canRotate = (JetpackRunning || !((m_currentCharacterState == HkCharacterStateType.HK_CHARACTER_IN_AIR || (int)m_currentCharacterState == MyCharacter.HK_CHARACTER_FLYING) && (m_currentJumpTime <= 0))) && (m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died);
2846 
2847  float acceleration = 0;
2848  float lastSpeed = m_currentSpeed;
2849  if (JetpackRunning)
2850  {
2851  JetpackComp.MoveAndRotate(ref moveIndicator, ref rotationIndicator, roll, canRotate);
2852  }
2853  else if (canMove || m_movementsFlagsChanged)
2854  {
2855  if (moveIndicator.LengthSquared() > 0)
2856  moveIndicator = Vector3.Normalize(moveIndicator);
2857 
2858  MyCharacterMovementEnum newMovementState = GetNewMovementState(ref moveIndicator, ref rotationIndicator, ref acceleration, sprint, walk, canMove, m_movementsFlagsChanged);
2859  SwitchAnimation(newMovementState);
2860 
2861  m_movementsFlagsChanged = false;
2862 
2863  SetCurrentMovementState(newMovementState);
2864  if (newMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting && StatComp != null)
2865  {
2866  StatComp.ApplyModifier("Sprint");
2867  }
2868 
2869  if (!IsIdle)
2870  m_currentWalkDelay = MathHelper.Clamp(m_currentWalkDelay - VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS, 0, m_currentWalkDelay);
2871 
2872  if (canMove)
2873  {
2874  float relativeSpeed = 1.0f;
2875  m_currentSpeed = LimitMaxSpeed(m_currentSpeed + (m_currentWalkDelay <= 0 ? acceleration * VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS : 0), m_currentMovementState, relativeSpeed);
2876  }
2877 
2878  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
2879  {
2880  Physics.CharacterProxy.PosX = m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting ? -moveIndicator.X : 0;
2881  Physics.CharacterProxy.PosY = moveIndicator.Z;
2882  Physics.CharacterProxy.Elevate = 0;
2883  }
2884 
2885  if (canMove && m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump)
2886  {
2887  int sign = Math.Sign(m_currentSpeed);
2888  m_currentSpeed += -sign * m_currentDecceleration * VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2889 
2890  if (Math.Sign(sign) != Math.Sign(m_currentSpeed))
2891  m_currentSpeed = 0;
2892  }
2893 
2894  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
2895  Physics.CharacterProxy.Speed = m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died ? m_currentSpeed : 0;
2896 
2897  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null && Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody() != null)
2898  {
2899 
2900  if ((jump && m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump))
2901  {
2902  PlayCharacterAnimation("Jump", MyBlendOption.Immediate, MyFrameOption.StayOnLastFrame, 0.0f, 1.3f);
2903 
2904  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
2905  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("jump", true);
2906 
2907  if (StatComp != null)
2908  {
2909  StatComp.DoAction("Jump");
2910  StatComp.ApplyModifier("Jump");
2911  }
2912  m_currentJumpTime = JUMP_DURATION;
2913  SetCurrentMovementState(MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump);
2914 
2915  m_canJump = false;
2916 
2917  m_frictionBeforeJump = Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody().Friction;
2918  // Modified jumping velocity, no need to apply force
2919  //Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody().ApplyForce(1, WorldMatrix.Up * Definition.JumpForce * MyPerGameSettings.CharacterGravityMultiplier * Physics.Mass);
2920  Physics.CharacterProxy.Jump = true;
2921  }
2922 
2923  //VRage.Trace.MyTrace.Send(VRage.Trace.TraceWindow.Default, "jump");
2924 
2925 
2926 
2927  if (m_currentJumpTime > 0)
2928  {
2929  m_currentJumpTime -= VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
2930 
2931  Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody().Friction = 0;
2932  Vector3 rotatedVector = WorldMatrix.Forward * -moveIndicator.Z + WorldMatrix.Right * moveIndicator.X;
2933  // Modified jumping velocity, no need to apply velocity
2934  //Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody().ApplyForce(1, rotatedVector * AERIAL_CONTROL_FORCE_MULTIPLIER * Physics.Mass);
2935  }
2936  else // If still falling, check if finished.
2937  {
2938  MyCharacterMovementEnum afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing;
2939 
2940  // Restore friction setting upon end-of-jump time.
2941  Physics.CharacterProxy.GetHitRigidBody().Friction = m_frictionBeforeJump;
2942 
2943  // If started falling in physics, set the char to correct state.
2944  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null && (Physics.CharacterProxy.GetState() == HkCharacterStateType.HK_CHARACTER_IN_AIR || (int)Physics.CharacterProxy.GetState() == MyCharacter.HK_CHARACTER_FLYING))
2945  {
2946  StartFalling();
2947  }
2948  // Didn't have time to start falling. Ex. landed on a mountain before started falling.
2949  else
2950  {
2951  if ((moveIndicator.X != 0 || moveIndicator.Z != 0))
2952  {
2953  if (!WantsCrouch)
2954  {
2955  if (moveIndicator.Z < 0)
2956  {
2957  if (sprint)
2958  {
2959  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting;
2960  PlayCharacterAnimation("Sprint", MyBlendOption.WaitForPreviousEnd, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.2f);
2961  }
2962  else
2963  {
2964  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.Walking;

2968  else
2969  {
2970  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.BackWalking;
2971  PlayCharacterAnimation("WalkBack", MyBlendOption.WaitForPreviousEnd, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.5f);
2972  }
2973  }
2974  else
2975  {
2976  if (moveIndicator.Z < 0)
2977  {
2978  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalking;
2979  PlayCharacterAnimation("CrouchWalk", MyBlendOption.WaitForPreviousEnd, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.2f);
2980  }
2981  else
2982  {
2983  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchBackWalking;
2984  PlayCharacterAnimation("CrouchWalkBack", MyBlendOption.WaitForPreviousEnd, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.2f);
2985  }
2986  }
2987  }
2988  else
2989  {
2990  afterJumpState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing;
2991  PlayCharacterAnimation("Idle", MyBlendOption.WaitForPreviousEnd, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.2f);
2992  }
2993 
2994  if (!m_canJump)
2995  SoundComp.PlayFallSound();
2996  m_canJump = true;
2997  SetCurrentMovementState(afterJumpState);
2998  }
2999 
3000  m_currentJumpTime = 0;
3001  }
3002  }
3003  }
3004  else if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
3005  {
3006  Physics.CharacterProxy.Elevate = 0;
3007  }
3008 
3009  if (!JetpackRunning)
3010  {
3011  if (rotationIndicator.Y != 0 && (canRotate || m_isFalling || m_currentJumpTime > 0) && Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
3012  {
3013  MatrixD rotationMatrix = MatrixD.CreateRotationY((-rotationIndicator.Y * RotationSpeed * CHARACTER_Y_ROTATION_FACTOR));
3014  MatrixD characterMatrix = MatrixD.CreateWorld(Physics.CharacterProxy.Position, Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward, Physics.CharacterProxy.Up);
3015  Vector3D headBoneTranslation = Vector3D.Zero;
3016 
3017  characterMatrix = rotationMatrix * characterMatrix;
3018 
3019  Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward = characterMatrix.Forward;
3020  Physics.CharacterProxy.Up = characterMatrix.Up;
3021  }
3022 
3023  if (rotationIndicator.X != 0)
3024  {

3026  ||
3027  (m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died))

3071  private List<HkBodyCollision> m_penetrationList = new List<HkBodyCollision>();
3072 
3073  public bool CanPlaceCharacter(ref MatrixD worldMatrix, bool useCharacterCenter = false, bool checkCharacters = false)
3074  {
3075  Vector3D translation = worldMatrix.Translation;
3076  Quaternion rotation = Quaternion.CreateFromRotationMatrix(worldMatrix);
3077 
3078  if (Physics == null || Physics.CharacterProxy == null && Physics.RigidBody == null)
3079  return true;
3080 
3081  m_penetrationList.Clear();
3082 
3083  if (!useCharacterCenter)
3084  {
3085  Vector3D transformedCenter = Vector3D.TransformNormal(Physics.Center, WorldMatrix);
3086  translation += transformedCenter;
3087  }
3088 
3089  //Check for grids
3090  m_penetrationList.Clear();
3091  MyPhysics.GetPenetrationsShape(Physics.CharacterProxy != null ? Physics.CharacterProxy.GetCollisionShape() : Physics.RigidBody.GetShape(), ref translation, ref rotation, m_penetrationList, MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.CharacterCollisionLayer);
3092  bool somethingHit = false;
3093  foreach (var collision in m_penetrationList)
3094  {
3095  IMyEntity collisionEntity = collision.GetCollisionEntity();
3096  if (collisionEntity != null)
3097  {
3098  if (collisionEntity.Physics == null)
3099  {
3100  Debug.Fail("CanPlaceCharacter found Entity with no physics: " + collisionEntity);
3101  MyLog.Default.WriteLine("CanPlaceCharacter found Entity with no physics: " + collisionEntity);
3102  }
3103  else if (!collisionEntity.Physics.IsPhantom)
3104  {
3105  somethingHit = true;
3106  break;
3107  }
3108  }
3109  else if (checkCharacters)
3110  {
3111  somethingHit = true;
3112  break;
3113  }
3114  }
3115 
3116  if (MySession.Static.VoxelMaps == null)
3117  return true;
3118 
3119  if (!somethingHit)
3120  { //Check for voxels
3121  BoundingSphereD sphere = new BoundingSphereD(worldMatrix.Translation, 0.75f);
3122  var overlappedVoxelmap = MySession.Static.VoxelMaps.GetOverlappingWithSphere(ref sphere);
3123  somethingHit = overlappedVoxelmap != null;
3124  }
3125 
3126  return !somethingHit;
3127  }

3154  internal void SetCurrentMovementState(MyCharacterMovementEnum state)
3155  {
3156  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died || m_currentMovementState == state, "Trying to set a new movement state, but character is in dead state!");
3157 
3158  if (m_currentMovementState == state)
3159  return;
3160 
3161  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
3162  {
3163  switch (state)
3164  {
3165  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Crouching:
3166  Physics.CharacterProxy.SetShapeForCrouch(Physics.HavokWorld, true);
3167  break;
3168 
3169  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingLeft:
3170  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingRight:
3171  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalking:
3172  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchBackWalking:
3173  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftBack:
3174  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightBack:
3175  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftFront:
3176  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightFront:
3177  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingLeft:
3178  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingRight:
3179  Physics.CharacterProxy.SetShapeForCrouch(Physics.HavokWorld, true);
3180  break;
3181 
3182  default:
3183  Physics.CharacterProxy.SetShapeForCrouch(Physics.HavokWorld, false);
3184  break;
3185  }
3186  }
3187 
3188  m_previousMovementState = m_currentMovementState;
3189  m_currentMovementState = state;
3190  if (OnMovementStateChanged != null)
3191  OnMovementStateChanged(m_previousMovementState, m_currentMovementState);
3192  }

3482  private MyCharacterMovementEnum GetNewMovementState(ref Vector3 moveIndicator, ref Vector2 rotationIndicator, ref float acceleration, bool sprint, bool walk, bool canMove, bool movementFlagsChanged)
3483  {
3484  // OM: Once dead, always dead, no resurrection in the game :-)
3485  if (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died)
3486  {
3487  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died;
3488  }
3489 
3490  MyCharacterMovementEnum newMovementState = m_currentMovementState;
3491 
3492  if (Definition.UseOnlyWalking)
3493  walk = true;
3494 
3495  if (m_currentJumpTime > 0f)
3496  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump;
3497 
3498  if (JetpackRunning)
3499  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.Flying;
3500 
3501  bool canWalk = true;
3502  bool canRun = true;
3503  bool canSprint = true;
3504  bool canMoveInternal = true;
3505  bool continuousWalk = false;
3506  bool continuousRun = false;
3507  bool continuousSprint = false;
3508 
3509  var currentState = m_currentMovementState;
3510  switch (currentState)
3511  {
3512  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Walking:
3513  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftBack:
3514  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftFront:
3515  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightBack:
3516  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightFront:
3517  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingLeft:
3518  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingRight:
3519  continuousWalk = true;
3520  break;
3521 
3522  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Running:
3523  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftBack:
3524  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftFront:
3525  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightBack:
3526  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightFront:
3527  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingLeft:
3528  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingRight:
3529  continuousRun = true;
3530  break;
3531 
3532  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting:
3533  continuousSprint = true;
3534  break;
3535  }
3536 
3537  MyTuple<ushort, MyStringHash> message;
3538  if (StatComp != null)
3539  {
3540  canWalk = StatComp.CanDoAction("Walk", out message, continuousWalk);
3541  canRun = StatComp.CanDoAction("Run", out message, continuousRun);
3542  canSprint = StatComp.CanDoAction("Sprint", out message, continuousSprint);
3543 
3544  if (MySession.Static != null && MySession.Static.LocalCharacter == this && message.Item1 == MyStatLogic.STAT_VALUE_TOO_LOW && message.Item2.String.CompareTo("Stamina") == 0)
3545  {
3546  m_notEnoughStatNotification.SetTextFormatArguments(message.Item2);
3547  MyHud.Notifications.Add(m_notEnoughStatNotification);
3548  }
3549 
3550  canMoveInternal = canWalk || canRun || canSprint;
3551  }
3552 
3553  bool moving = ((moveIndicator.X != 0 || moveIndicator.Z != 0) && canMove && canMoveInternal);
3554  bool rotating = rotationIndicator.X != 0 || rotationIndicator.Y != 0;
3555 
3556  if (moving || movementFlagsChanged)
3557  {
3558  if (sprint && canSprint)
3559  {
3560  newMovementState = GetSprintState(ref moveIndicator);
3561  }
3562  else
3563  {
3564  if (moving)
3565  {
3566  if (walk && canWalk)
3567  newMovementState = GetWalkingState(ref moveIndicator);
3568  else if (canRun)
3569  newMovementState = GetRunningState(ref moveIndicator);
3570  else
3571  newMovementState = GetWalkingState(ref moveIndicator);
3572  }
3573  else
3574  {
3575  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3576  }
3577  }
3578 
3579  acceleration = GetMovementAcceleration(newMovementState);
3580  m_currentDecceleration = 0;
3581  }
3582  else
3583  if (rotating)
3584  {
3585  const float ANGLE_FOR_ROTATION_ANIMATION = 20;
3586 
3587  if ((Math.Abs(rotationIndicator.Y) > ANGLE_FOR_ROTATION_ANIMATION) &&
3588  (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing || m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Crouching)
3589  )
3590  {
3591  if (WantsCrouch)
3592  {
3593  if (rotationIndicator.Y > 0)
3594  {
3595  newMovementState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingRight;
3596  }
3597  else
3598  {
3599  newMovementState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingLeft;
3600  }
3601  }
3602  else
3603  {
3604  if (rotationIndicator.Y > 0)
3605  {
3606  newMovementState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingRight;
3607  }
3608  else
3609  {
3610  newMovementState = MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingLeft;
3611  }
3612  }
3613  }
3614  }
3615  else
3616  {
3617  switch (m_currentMovementState)
3618  {
3619  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Walking:
3620  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftFront:
3621  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightFront:
3622  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.BackWalking:
3623  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftBack:
3624  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightBack:
3625  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingLeft:
3626  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingRight:
3627  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Running:
3628  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftFront:
3629  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightFront:
3630  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Backrunning:
3631  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftBack:
3632  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightBack:
3633  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingLeft:
3634  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingRight:
3635  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalking:
3636  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftFront:
3637  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightFront:
3638  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchBackWalking:
3639  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftBack:
3640  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightBack:
3641  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingLeft:
3642  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingRight:
3643  {
3644  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3645  m_currentDecceleration = MyPerGameSettings.CharacterMovement.WalkDecceleration;
3646 
3647  break;
3648  }
3649 
3650  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting:
3651  {
3652  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3653 
3654  m_currentDecceleration = MyPerGameSettings.CharacterMovement.SprintDecceleration;
3655 
3656  break;
3657  }
3658 
3659  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing:
3660  {
3661  if (WantsCrouch)
3662  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3663 
3664  break;
3665  }
3666 
3667  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Crouching:
3668  {
3669  if (!WantsCrouch)
3670  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3671 
3672  break;
3673  }
3674 
3675  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Flying:
3676  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump:
3677  break;
3678 
3679  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingLeft:
3680  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingRight:
3681  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingLeft:
3682  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingRight:
3683  newMovementState = GetIdleState();
3684  break;
3685 
3686  default:
3687  //System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(false, "Unknown movement state");
3688  break;
3689  }
3690  }
3691 
3692  return newMovementState;
3693  }

3695  internal float LimitMaxSpeed(float currentSpeed, MyCharacterMovementEnum movementState, float serverRatio)
3696  {
3697  float limitedSpeed = currentSpeed;
3698  switch (movementState)
3699  {
3700  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Running:
3701  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Flying:
3702  {
3703  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxRunSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxRunSpeed * serverRatio);
3704  break;
3705  }
3706 
3707  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Walking:
3708  {
3709  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxWalkSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxWalkSpeed * serverRatio);
3710  break;
3711  }
3712 
3713  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.BackWalking:
3714  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftBack:
3715  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightBack:
3716  {
3717  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxBackwalkSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxBackwalkSpeed * serverRatio);
3718  break;
3719  }
3720 
3721  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingLeft:
3722  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingRight:
3723  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingLeftFront:
3724  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightFront:
3725  {
3726  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxWalkStrafingSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxWalkStrafingSpeed * serverRatio);
3727  break;
3728  }
3729 
3730  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Backrunning:
3731  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftBack:
3732  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightBack:
3733  {
3734  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxBackrunSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxBackrunSpeed * serverRatio);
3735  break;
3736  }
3737 
3738  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingLeft:
3739  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunStrafingRight:
3740  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningLeftFront:
3741  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RunningRightFront:
3742  {
3743  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxRunStrafingSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxRunStrafingSpeed * serverRatio);
3744  break;
3745  }
3746 
3747  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalking:
3748  {
3749  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxCrouchWalkSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxCrouchWalkSpeed * serverRatio);
3750  break;
3751  }
3752 
3753  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingLeft:
3754  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingRight:
3755  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftFront:
3756  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightFront:
3757  {
3758  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxCrouchStrafingSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxCrouchStrafingSpeed * serverRatio);
3759  break;
3760  }
3761 
3762  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchBackWalking:
3763  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingLeftBack:
3764  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchWalkingRightBack:
3765  {
3766  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxCrouchBackwalkSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxCrouchBackwalkSpeed * serverRatio);
3767  break;
3768  }
3769 
3770  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sprinting:
3771  {
3772  limitedSpeed = MathHelper.Clamp(currentSpeed, -Definition.MaxSprintSpeed * serverRatio, Definition.MaxSprintSpeed * serverRatio);
3773  break;
3774  }
3775 
3776  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump:
3777  {
3778  break;
3779  }
3780 
3781  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing:
3782  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Crouching:
3783  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sitting:
3784  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingLeft:
3785  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.RotatingRight:
3786  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingLeft:
3787  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchRotatingRight:
3788  case MyCharacterMovementEnum.Falling:
3789  break;
3790 
3791  default:
3792  {
3793  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(false);
3794  break;
3795  }
3796  }
3797  return limitedSpeed;
3798  }

3801  {
3802  float blend = 0;
3803  if (m_currentAnimationChangeDelay > SAFE_DELAY_FOR_ANIMATION_BLEND)
3804  blend = idealBlend;
3805  m_currentAnimationChangeDelay = 0;
3806  return blend;
3807  }

3820  private MyCharacterMovementEnum GetWalkingState(ref Vector3 moveIndicator)
3821  {
3822  double tan23 = Math.Tan(MathHelper.ToRadians(23));
3823  if (Math.Abs(moveIndicator.X) < tan23 * Math.Abs(moveIndicator.Z))
3824  {
3825  if (moveIndicator.Z < 0)
3826  {
3827  if (!WantsCrouch)
3828  {

3845  }
3846  }
3847  }
3848  else if (Math.Abs(moveIndicator.X) * tan23 > Math.Abs(moveIndicator.Z))
3849  {
3850  if (moveIndicator.X > 0)
3851  {
3852  if (!WantsCrouch)
3853  {
3854  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingRight;
3855  }
3856  else
3857  {
3858  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingRight;
3859  }
3860  }
3861  else
3862  {
3863  if (!WantsCrouch)
3864  {
3865  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkStrafingLeft;
3866  }
3867  else
3868  {
3869  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.CrouchStrafingLeft;
3870  }
3871  }
3872  }
3873  else
3874  {
3875  if (moveIndicator.X > 0)
3876  {
3877  if (moveIndicator.Z < 0)
3878  {
3879  if (!WantsCrouch)
3880  {
3881  return MyCharacterMovementEnum.WalkingRightFront;
3882  }
3883  else
3884  {

4063  private bool UpdateCapsuleBones()
4064  {
4065  if (m_characterBoneCapsulesReady)
4066  return true;
4067 
4068  if (m_bodyCapsuleInfo == null || m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Count == 0)
4069  return false;
4070 
4071  if (this.Definition.Name == "Space_spider")
4072  MyRenderDebugInputComponent.Clear();
4073 
4074  var characterBones = AnimationController.CharacterBones;
4075 
4076  if (Physics.Ragdoll != null && Components.Has<MyCharacterRagdollComponent>())
4077  {
4078  // TODO: OM - This needs to be changed..
4079  // Create capsules with help of ragdoll model
4080  var ragdollComponent = Components.Get<MyCharacterRagdollComponent>();
4081  for (int i = 0; i < m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Count; i++)
4082  {
4083  var boneInfo = m_bodyCapsuleInfo[i];
4084  if (characterBones == null || boneInfo.Bone1 >= characterBones.Length || boneInfo.Bone2 >= characterBones.Length) // prevent crashes
4085  continue;
4086 
4087  var rigidBody = ragdollComponent.RagdollMapper.GetBodyBindedToBone(characterBones[boneInfo.Bone1]);
4088 
4089  MatrixD transformationMatrix = characterBones[boneInfo.Bone1].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix;
4090 
4091  var shape = rigidBody.GetShape();
4092 
4093  m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 = transformationMatrix.Translation;
4094  m_bodyCapsules[i].P1 = (characterBones[boneInfo.Bone2].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix).Translation;
4095  Vector3 difference = m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 - m_bodyCapsules[i].P1;
4096 
4097  if (difference.LengthSquared() < 0.05f)
4098  {
4099  if (shape.ShapeType == HkShapeType.Capsule)
4100  {
4101  var capsuleShape = (HkCapsuleShape)shape;
4102  m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 = Vector3.Transform(capsuleShape.VertexA, transformationMatrix);
4103  m_bodyCapsules[i].P1 = Vector3.Transform(capsuleShape.VertexB, transformationMatrix);
4104  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = capsuleShape.Radius * 0.8f;
4105  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
4106  {
4107  if (this.Definition.Name == "Space_spider")
4108  MyRenderDebugInputComponent.AddCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i], Color.Green);
4109  //MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i].P0, m_bodyCapsules[i].P1, m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius, Color.Green, false, false);
4110  }
4111  }
4112  else
4113  {
4114  Vector4 min4, max4;
4115  shape.GetLocalAABB(0.0001f, out min4, out max4);
4116  float distance = Math.Max(Math.Max(max4.X - min4.X, max4.Y - min4.Y), max4.Z - min4.Z) * 0.5f; // scalling because the aabb is always bigger
4117 
4118  m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 = transformationMatrix.Translation + (transformationMatrix.Left * distance * 0.25f);
4119  m_bodyCapsules[i].P1 = transformationMatrix.Translation + (transformationMatrix.Left * distance * 0.5f);
4120  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = distance * 0.25f;
4121  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
4122  {
4123  if (this.Definition.Name == "Space_spider")
4124  MyRenderDebugInputComponent.AddCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i], Color.Blue);
4125  //MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i].P0, m_bodyCapsules[i].P1, m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius, Color.Blue, false, false);
4126  }
4127  }
4128  }
4129  else
4130  {
4131  if (boneInfo.Radius != 0)
4132  {
4133  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = boneInfo.Radius;
4134  }
4135  else if (shape.ShapeType == HkShapeType.Capsule)
4136  {
4137  var capsuleShape = (HkCapsuleShape)shape;
4138  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = capsuleShape.Radius;
4139  }
4140  else
4141  {
4142  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = difference.Length() * 0.28f;
4143  }
4144 
4145  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
4146  {
4147  if (this.Definition.Name == "Space_spider")
4148  MyRenderDebugInputComponent.AddCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i], Color.Blue);
4149  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i].P0, m_bodyCapsules[i].P1, m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius, Color.Yellow, false, false);
4150  }
4151  }
4152  }
4153  }
4154  else
4155  {
4156  // Fallback to dynamically determined values for capsules
4157  for (int i = 0; i < m_bodyCapsuleInfo.Count; i++)
4158  {
4159  var capsuleInfo = m_bodyCapsuleInfo[i];
4160  if (characterBones == null || capsuleInfo.Bone1 >= characterBones.Length || capsuleInfo.Bone2 >= characterBones.Length) // prevent crashes
4161  continue;
4162 
4163  m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 = (characterBones[capsuleInfo.Bone1].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix).Translation;
4164  m_bodyCapsules[i].P1 = (characterBones[capsuleInfo.Bone2].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix).Translation;
4165  Vector3 difference = m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 - m_bodyCapsules[i].P1;
4166 
4167  if (capsuleInfo.Radius != 0)
4168  {
4169  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = capsuleInfo.Radius;
4170  }
4171  else if (difference.LengthSquared() < 0.05f)
4172  {
4173  m_bodyCapsules[i].P1 = m_bodyCapsules[i].P0 + (characterBones[capsuleInfo.Bone1].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix).Left * 0.1f;
4174  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = 0.1f;
4175  }
4176  else
4177  {
4178  m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius = difference.Length() * 0.3f;
4179  }
4180 
4181  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW && MyDebugDrawSettings.DEBUG_DRAW_SHOW_DAMAGE)
4182  {
4183  if (this.Definition.Name == "Space_spider")
4184  MyRenderDebugInputComponent.AddCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i], Color.Green);
4185  //MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(m_bodyCapsules[i].P0, m_bodyCapsules[i].P1, m_bodyCapsules[i].Radius, Color.Green, false, false);
4186  }
4187  }
4188  }
4189 
4190  m_characterBoneCapsulesReady = true;
4191  return true;
4192  }

4196  private MatrixD GetHeadMatrixInternal(int headBone, bool includeY, bool includeX = true, bool forceHeadAnim = false, bool forceHeadBone = false)
4197  {
4198  if (PositionComp == null)
4199  return MatrixD.Identity;
4200  //Matrix matrixRotation = Matrix.Identity;
4201  MatrixD matrixRotation = MatrixD.Identity;
4202 
4203  bool useAnimationInsteadX = ShouldUseAnimatedHeadRotation() && (!JetpackRunning || IsLocalHeadAnimationInProgress()) || forceHeadAnim;
4204 
4205  if (includeX && !useAnimationInsteadX)
4206  matrixRotation = MatrixD.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3D.Right, MathHelper.ToRadians(m_headLocalXAngle));
4207 
4208  if (includeY)
4209  matrixRotation = matrixRotation * Matrix.CreateFromAxisAngle(Vector3.Up, MathHelper.ToRadians(m_headLocalYAngle));
4210 
4211  Vector3 averageBob = Vector3.Zero;

4214  // headbob would be redone later
4215  //if (MySandboxGame.Config.DisableHeadbob && !forceHeadBone && !ForceFirstPersonCamera)
4216  //{
4217  // foreach (var headTranslation in m_bobQueue)
4218  // {
4219  // averageBob += headTranslation;
4220  // }
4221  // if (m_bobQueue.Count > 0)
4222  // averageBob /= m_bobQueue.Count;
4223  //}
4224  //else
4225  {
4226  if (headBone != -1)
4227  {
4228  averageBob = BoneAbsoluteTransforms[headBone].Translation;
4229  float applyIkOneHeadBoneWeight = 1 - (float)Math.Cos(MathHelper.ToRadians(m_headLocalXAngle)); // the headbone should be ignored by IK, but here, we need to reapply it to have correct distance from ground when looking down
4230  averageBob.Y += applyIkOneHeadBoneWeight * AnimationController.InverseKinematics.RootBoneVerticalOffset;
4231  }
4232  }
4233 
4234  //if (this.ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled() && sync)
4235  //{
4236  // m_averageBob = averageBob;
4237  //}
4238  //else if (this.ControllerInfo.IsRemotelyControlled() && Sync.IsServer)
4239  //{
4240  // averageBob = m_averageBob;
4241  //}
4242 
4243  if (useAnimationInsteadX && headBone != -1
4244  && BoneAbsoluteTransforms[headBone].Right.LengthSquared() > float.Epsilon // MZ: fixing NaN issue
4245  && BoneAbsoluteTransforms[headBone].Up.LengthSquared() > float.Epsilon
4246  && BoneAbsoluteTransforms[headBone].Forward.LengthSquared() > float.Epsilon)
4247  {
4248  //m_headMatrix = Matrix.CreateRotationX(-(float)Math.PI * 0.5f) * /* Matrix.CreateRotationY(-(float)Math.PI * 0.5f) */ Matrix.Normalize(BoneTransformsWrite[HEAD_DUMMY_BONE]);
4249  Matrix hm = Matrix.Identity;// Matrix.Normalize(BoneAbsoluteTransforms[headBone]);
4250  hm.Translation = averageBob;
4251  m_headMatrix = MatrixD.CreateRotationX(-Math.PI * 0.5) * hm;
4252  }
4253  else
4254  {
4255  //m_headMatrix = Matrix.CreateTranslation(BoneTransformsWrite[HEAD_DUMMY_BONE].Translation);
4256  m_headMatrix = MatrixD.CreateTranslation(0, averageBob.Y, averageBob.Z);
4257  }
4258

4260  //headPosition.Translation += WorldMatrix.Up * 0.04f;
4261  //Vector3 translation = Vector3.Transform(headPosition, WorldMatrix);
4262 
4263  //Orient direction to some point in front of char
4264  Vector3D imagPoint = PositionComp.GetPosition() + WorldMatrix.Up + WorldMatrix.Forward * 10;
4265  Vector3 imagDir = Vector3.Normalize(imagPoint - headPosition.Translation);
4266 
4267  MatrixD orientMatrix = MatrixD.CreateFromDir((Vector3D)imagDir, WorldMatrix.Up);
4268 
4269  MatrixD matrix = m_headMatrix * matrixRotation * orientMatrix;
4270  matrix.Translation = headPosition.Translation;
4271 
4272  return matrix;
4273  }
