4305  public override MatrixD GetViewMatrix()
4306  {
4307  if (IsDead && MyPerGameSettings.SwitchToSpectatorCameraAfterDeath)
4308  {
4309  m_isInFirstPersonView = false;
4310  if (m_lastCorrectSpectatorCamera == MatrixD.Zero)
4311  {
4312  m_lastCorrectSpectatorCamera = MatrixD.CreateLookAt(WorldMatrix.Translation + 2 * Vector3.Up - 2 * Vector3.Forward, WorldMatrix.Translation, Vector3.Up);
4313  }
4314  Vector3 camPosition = MatrixD.Invert(m_lastCorrectSpectatorCamera).Translation;
4315  Vector3 target = WorldMatrix.Translation;
4316  if (m_headBoneIndex != -1)
4317  {
4318  target = Vector3.Transform(AnimationController.CharacterBones[m_headBoneIndex].AbsoluteTransform.Translation, WorldMatrix);
4319  }
4320  MatrixD viewMatrix = MatrixD.CreateLookAt(camPosition, target, Vector3.Up);
4321  return viewMatrix.IsValid() && viewMatrix != MatrixD.Zero ? viewMatrix : m_lastCorrectSpectatorCamera;
4322  }
4323 
4324  if (!m_isInFirstPersonView)
4325  {
4326  //Matrix viewMatrix = Get3rdCameraMatrix(false, true);
4327  bool lastForceFirstPersonCamera = ForceFirstPersonCamera;
4328  ForceFirstPersonCamera = !MyThirdPersonSpectator.Static.IsCameraPositionOk();
4329  if (!ForceFirstPersonCamera)
4330  {
4331  if (m_switchBackToSpectatorTimer > 0)
4332  {
4333  m_switchBackToSpectatorTimer -= VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
4334  ForceFirstPersonCamera = true;
4335  }
4336  else
4337  {
4338  m_switchBackToFirstPersonTimer = CAMERA_SWITCH_DELAY;
4339  return MyThirdPersonSpectator.Static.GetViewMatrix();
4340  }
4341  }
4342  else
4343  {
4344  if (m_switchBackToFirstPersonTimer > 0)
4345  {
4346  m_switchBackToFirstPersonTimer -= VRage.Game.MyEngineConstants.UPDATE_STEP_SIZE_IN_SECONDS;
4347  ForceFirstPersonCamera = false;
4348  return MyThirdPersonSpectator.Static.GetViewMatrix();
4349  }
4350  else
4351  {
4352  m_switchBackToSpectatorTimer = CAMERA_SWITCH_DELAY;
4353  }
4354  }
4355  }
4356 
4357  MatrixD matrix = GetHeadMatrix(false, true, preferLocalOverSync: true);
4358  matrix.Translation = matrix.Translation;// +m_headSafeOffset;
4359 
4360  if (IsDead)
4361  {
4362  Vector3 halfExtents = new Vector3(Definition.CharacterHeadSize * 0.5f);
4363  Vector3D headPos = matrix.Translation;
4364  m_penetrationList.Clear();
4365  MyPhysics.GetPenetrationsBox(ref halfExtents, ref headPos, ref Quaternion.Identity, m_penetrationList, 0);
4366 
4367  foreach (var item in m_penetrationList)
4368  {
4369  if (item.GetCollisionEntity() is MyVoxelBase)
4370  {
4371  Vector3D directionAgainstGravity = -MyGravityProviderSystem.CalculateTotalGravityInPoint(headPos);
4372  directionAgainstGravity.Normalize();
4373  directionAgainstGravity *= 0.3f;
4374  matrix.Translation += directionAgainstGravity;
4375  break;
4376  }
4377  }
4378  }
4379 
4380  m_lastCorrectSpectatorCamera = MatrixD.Zero;
4381 
4382  return MatrixD.Invert(matrix);
4383  }

4395  public bool GetIntersectionWithLine(ref LineD line, ref MyCharacterHitInfo info, IntersectionFlags flags = IntersectionFlags.ALL_TRIANGLES)
4396  {
4397  // TODO: This now uses caspule of physics rigid body on the character, it needs to be changed to ragdoll
4398  // Currently this approach will be used to support Characters with different skeleton than humanoid
4399  if (info == null)
4400  info = new MyCharacterHitInfo();
4401 
4402  info.Reset();
4403 
4404  bool capsulesReady = UpdateCapsuleBones();
4405  if (!capsulesReady)
4406  return false;
4407 
4408  double closestDistanceToHit = double.MaxValue;
4409 
4410  Vector3D hitPosition = Vector3D.Zero;
4411  Vector3D hitPosition2 = Vector3D.Zero;
4412  Vector3 hitNormal = Vector3.Zero;
4413  Vector3 hitNormal2 = Vector3.Zero;
4414 
4415  int capsuleIndex = -1;
4416  for (int i = 0; i < m_bodyCapsules.Length; i++)
4417  {
4418  CapsuleD capsule = m_bodyCapsules[i];
4419  if (capsule.Intersect(line, ref hitPosition, ref hitPosition2, ref hitNormal, ref hitNormal2))
4420  {
4421  double distanceToHit = Vector3.Distance(hitPosition, line.From);
4422  if (distanceToHit >= closestDistanceToHit)
4423  continue;
4424 
4425  closestDistanceToHit = distanceToHit;
4426  capsuleIndex = i;
4427  }
4428  }
4429 
4430  if (capsuleIndex != -1)
4431  {
4432  Matrix worldMatrix = PositionComp.WorldMatrix;
4433  int boneIndex = FindBestBone(capsuleIndex, ref hitPosition, ref worldMatrix);
4434 
4435  // Transform line to model static position and compute accurate collision there
4436  // 1. Transform line in local coordinates (used later)
4437  Matrix worldMatrixInv = PositionComp.WorldMatrixNormalizedInv;
4438  Vector3 fromTrans = Vector3.Transform(line.From, ref worldMatrixInv);
4439  Vector3 toTrans = Vector3.Transform(line.To, ref worldMatrixInv);
4440  LineD lineLocal = new LineD(fromTrans, toTrans);
4441 
4442  // 2. Transform line to to bone pose in binding position
4443  var bone = AnimationController.CharacterBones[boneIndex];
4444  bone.ComputeAbsoluteTransform();
4445  Matrix boneAbsTrans = bone.AbsoluteTransform;
4446  Matrix skinTransform = bone.SkinTransform;
4447  Matrix boneTrans = skinTransform * boneAbsTrans;
4448  Matrix invBoneTrans = Matrix.Invert(boneTrans);
4449  fromTrans = Vector3.Transform(fromTrans, ref invBoneTrans);
4450  toTrans = Vector3.Transform(toTrans, ref invBoneTrans);
4451 
4452  // 3. Move back line to world coordinates
4453  LineD lineTransWorld = new LineD(Vector3.Transform(fromTrans, ref worldMatrix), Vector3.Transform(toTrans, ref worldMatrix));
4454  MyIntersectionResultLineTriangleEx? triangle_;
4455  bool success = base.GetIntersectionWithLine(ref lineTransWorld, out triangle_, flags);
4456  if (success)
4457  {
4458  MyIntersectionResultLineTriangleEx triangle = triangle_.Value;
4459 
4460  info.CapsuleIndex = capsuleIndex;
4461  info.BoneIndex = boneIndex;
4462  info.Capsule = m_bodyCapsules[info.CapsuleIndex];
4463  info.HitHead = info.CapsuleIndex == 0 && m_bodyCapsules.Length > 1;
4464  info.HitPositionBindingPose = triangle.IntersectionPointInObjectSpace;
4465  info.HitNormalBindingPose = triangle.NormalInObjectSpace;
4466  info.BindingTransformation = boneTrans;
4467 
4468  // 4. Move intersection from binding to dynamic pose
4469  MyTriangle_Vertices vertices = new MyTriangle_Vertices();
4470  vertices.Vertex0 = Vector3.Transform(triangle.Triangle.InputTriangle.Vertex0, ref boneTrans);
4471  vertices.Vertex1 = Vector3.Transform(triangle.Triangle.InputTriangle.Vertex1, ref boneTrans);
4472  vertices.Vertex2 = Vector3.Transform(triangle.Triangle.InputTriangle.Vertex2, ref boneTrans);
4473  Vector3 triangleNormal = Vector3.TransformNormal(triangle.Triangle.InputTriangleNormal, boneTrans);
4474  MyIntersectionResultLineTriangle triraw = new MyIntersectionResultLineTriangle(triangle.Triangle.TriangleIndex, ref vertices, ref triangle.Triangle.BoneWeights, ref triangleNormal, triangle.Triangle.Distance);
4475 
4476  Vector3 intersectionLocal = Vector3.Transform(triangle.IntersectionPointInObjectSpace, ref boneTrans);
4477  Vector3 normalLocal = Vector3.TransformNormal(triangle.NormalInObjectSpace, boneTrans);
4478 
4479  // 5. Store results
4480  triangle = new MyIntersectionResultLineTriangleEx();
4481  triangle.Triangle = triraw;
4482  triangle.IntersectionPointInObjectSpace = intersectionLocal;
4483  triangle.NormalInObjectSpace = normalLocal;
4484  triangle.IntersectionPointInWorldSpace = Vector3.Transform(intersectionLocal, ref worldMatrix);
4485  triangle.NormalInWorldSpace = Vector3.TransformNormal(normalLocal, worldMatrix);
4486  triangle.InputLineInObjectSpace = lineLocal;
4487 
4488  info.Triangle = triangle;
4489 
4490  if (MyDebugDrawSettings.ENABLE_DEBUG_DRAW)
4491  {
4492  MyRenderProxy.DebugClearPersistentMessages();
4493  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(info.Capsule.P0, info.Capsule.P1, info.Capsule.Radius, Color.Aqua, false, persistent: true);
4494 
4495  Vector3 p0Local = Vector3.Transform(info.Capsule.P0, ref worldMatrixInv);
4496  Vector3 p1Local = Vector3.Transform(info.Capsule.P1, ref worldMatrixInv);
4497  Vector3 p0LocalTrans = Vector3.Transform(p0Local, ref invBoneTrans);
4498  Vector3 p1LocalTrans = Vector3.Transform(p1Local, ref invBoneTrans);
4499  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawCapsule(Vector3.Transform(p0LocalTrans, ref worldMatrix), Vector3.Transform(p1LocalTrans, ref worldMatrix), info.Capsule.Radius, Color.Brown, false, persistent: true);
4500 
4501  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawLine3D(line.From, line.To, Color.Blue, Color.Red, false, true);
4502  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawLine3D(lineTransWorld.From, lineTransWorld.To, Color.Green, Color.Yellow, false, true);
4503  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawSphere(triangle.IntersectionPointInWorldSpace, 0.02f, Color.Red, 1, false, persistent: true);
4504  MyRenderProxy.DebugDrawAxis((MatrixD)boneTrans * WorldMatrix, 0.1f, false, true, true);
4505  }
4506 
4507  return true;
4508  }
4509  }
4510 
4511  return false;
4512  }
4513 
4517  private int FindBestBone(int capsuleIndex, ref Vector3D hitPosition, ref Matrix worldMatrix)
4518  {
4519  MyBoneCapsuleInfo info = m_bodyCapsuleInfo[capsuleIndex];
4520  CapsuleD capsule = m_bodyCapsules[capsuleIndex];
4521  MyCharacterBone ascendant = AnimationController.CharacterBones[info.AscendantBone];
4522  MyCharacterBone descendant = AnimationController.CharacterBones[info.DescendantBone];
4523 
4524  Vector3D p0_p1 = Vector3.Normalize(capsule.P0 - capsule.P1);
4525  double p0_p1Len = p0_p1.Length();
4526  Vector3D hit_p1 = hitPosition - capsule.P1;
4527  double hitProjectionInAxis = Vector3D.Dot(hit_p1, p0_p1) / p0_p1Len;
4528 
4529  int prevIndex = descendant.Index;
4530  double currDistance = 0;
4531  MyCharacterBone bone = descendant.Parent;
4532  while (true)
4533  {
4534  if (hitProjectionInAxis < currDistance || prevIndex == ascendant.Index)
4535  {
4536  // Second condition is we reached last bone
4537  break;
4538  }
4539 
4540  Vector3 tbone = Vector3.Transform(bone.AbsoluteTransform.Translation, ref worldMatrix);
4541  Vector3D tbone_p1 = tbone - capsule.P1;
4542  currDistance = Vector3D.Dot(tbone_p1, p0_p1) / p0_p1Len;
4543 
4544  prevIndex = bone.Index;
4545  bone = bone.Parent;
4546  if (bone == null)
4547  {
4548  Debug.Assert(false, "In capsule with index " + capsuleIndex + ", bone1 must be in the same branch as bone2");
4549  break;
4550  }
4551  }
4552 
4553  return prevIndex;
4554  }

4641  if (MySession.Static.ControlledEntity == this && m_currentWeapon != null)

4989  {
4990  MyDefinitionId? weaponDefinition = null;
4991  if (weapon != null)
4992  weaponDefinition = weapon.Definition.Id;
4993  // CH:TODO: This part of code seems to do nothing
4994  if (weaponDefinition.HasValue && m_rightHandItemBone == -1)
4995  return;
4996 
4997  if (WeaponTakesBuilderFromInventory(weaponDefinition))
4998  {
4999  MyPhysicalInventoryItem? item = null;
5000  if (inventoryItemId.HasValue)
5001  {
5002  item = this.GetInventory().GetItemByID(inventoryItemId.Value);
5003  }
5004  else
5005  {
5006  item = FindWeaponItemByDefinition(weaponDefinition.Value);
5007  }
5008  // This can pop-up after inventory truncation, which is OK. Uncomment for debugging
5009  //Debug.Assert(item != null, "Character switched to a weapon not in the inventory");
5010  if (item == null)
5011  return;
5012 
5013  Debug.Assert(item.Value.Content != null, "item.Value.Content was null in MyCharacter.SwitchToWeapon");
5014  if (item.Value.Content == null)
5015  {
5016  MySandboxGame.Log.WriteLine("item.Value.Content was null in MyCharacter.SwitchToWeapon");
5017  MySandboxGame.Log.WriteLine("item.Value = " + item.Value);
5018  MySandboxGame.Log.WriteLine("weaponDefinition.Value = " + weaponDefinition);
5019  return;
5020  }
5021 
5022  SwitchToWeaponInternal(weaponDefinition, true, item.Value.ItemId, 0);
5023  }
5024  else
5025  {
5026  SwitchToWeaponInternal(weaponDefinition, true, null, 0);
5027  }
5028  }
5029 
5030  private void SwitchToWeaponInternal(MyDefinitionId? weaponDefinition, bool updateSync, uint? inventoryItemId, long weaponEntityId)
5031  {
5032  if (updateSync)
5033  {
5034  Debug.Assert(weaponEntityId == 0);
5035  //Because while waiting for answer we dont want to shoot from old weapon
5036  UnequipWeapon();
5037 
5038  RequestSwitchToWeapon(weaponDefinition, inventoryItemId);
5039  return;
5040  }
5041 
5042  UnequipWeapon();
5043 
5044  StopCurrentWeaponShooting();
5045 
5046  MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase weaponEntityBuilder = GetObjectBuilderForWeapon(weaponDefinition, ref inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
5047  var gun = CreateGun(weaponEntityBuilder, inventoryItemId);
5048 
5049  EquipWeapon(gun);
5050 
5051  UpdateShadowIgnoredObjects();
5052  }
5053 
5054  private MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase GetObjectBuilderForWeapon(MyDefinitionId? weaponDefinition, ref uint? inventoryItemId, long weaponEntityId)
5055  {
5056  MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase weaponEntityBuilder = null;
5057  // On the server or your local client character, you have the inventory correct, so create the item from there
5058  if (inventoryItemId.HasValue && (Sync.IsServer || this.ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled()))
5059  {
5060  var inventory = this.GetInventory();
5061  var item = inventory.GetItemByID(inventoryItemId.Value);
5062  if (item.HasValue)
5063  {
5064  var physicalGunObject = item.Value.Content as MyObjectBuilder_PhysicalGunObject;
5065  if (physicalGunObject != null)
5066  {
5067  weaponEntityBuilder = physicalGunObject.GunEntity;
5068  }
5069 
5070  if (weaponEntityBuilder == null)
5071  {
5072  var handItemDef = MyDefinitionManager.Static.TryGetHandItemForPhysicalItem(weaponDefinition.Value);
5073  if (handItemDef != null)
5074  {
5075  weaponEntityBuilder = (MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase)MyObjectBuilderSerializer.CreateNewObject(handItemDef.Id);
5076  weaponEntityBuilder.EntityId = weaponEntityId;
5077  }
5078  }
5079  else
5080  {
5081  weaponEntityBuilder.EntityId = weaponEntityId;
5082  }
5083 
5084  if (physicalGunObject != null)
5085  {
5086  physicalGunObject.GunEntity = weaponEntityBuilder;
5087  }
5088  }
5089  }
5090  else
5091  {
5092  // Don't check inventory only if you're a client looking at someone else or if the weapon does not require it
5093  bool dontCheckInventory = (!Sync.IsServer && this.ControllerInfo.IsRemotelyControlled()) || !WeaponTakesBuilderFromInventory(weaponDefinition);
5094  if (weaponDefinition == null)
5095  {
5096  EquipWeapon(null);
5097  }
5098  else if (dontCheckInventory && weaponDefinition.Value.TypeId == typeof(MyObjectBuilder_PhysicalGunObject))
5099  {
5100  var handItemDef = MyDefinitionManager.Static.TryGetHandItemForPhysicalItem(weaponDefinition.Value);
5101 
5102  if (handItemDef != null)
5103  {
5104  weaponEntityBuilder = (MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase)MyObjectBuilderSerializer.CreateNewObject(handItemDef.Id);
5105  weaponEntityBuilder.EntityId = weaponEntityId;
5106  }
5107  }
5108  else
5109  {
5110  weaponEntityBuilder = MyObjectBuilderSerializer.CreateNewObject(weaponDefinition.Value.TypeId) as MyObjectBuilder_EntityBase;
5111  if (weaponEntityBuilder != null)
5112  {
5113  weaponEntityBuilder.EntityId = weaponEntityId;
5114  if (WeaponTakesBuilderFromInventory(weaponDefinition))
5115  {
5116  var item = FindWeaponItemByDefinition(weaponDefinition.Value);
5117  if (item.HasValue)
5118  {
5119  var physicalGunBuilder = item.Value.Content as MyObjectBuilder_PhysicalGunObject;
5120  if (physicalGunBuilder != null)
5121  physicalGunBuilder.GunEntity = weaponEntityBuilder;
5122  inventoryItemId = item.Value.ItemId;
5123  }
5124  }
5125  }
5126  else
5127  {
5128  Debug.Fail("Couldn't create builder for weapon! typeID: " + weaponDefinition.Value.TypeId.ToString());
5129  }
5130  }
5131  }
5132 
5133  if (weaponEntityBuilder != null)
5134  {
5135  var deviceBuilder = weaponEntityBuilder as IMyObjectBuilder_GunObject<MyObjectBuilder_DeviceBase>;
5136  if (deviceBuilder != null)
5137  {
5138  if (deviceBuilder.DeviceBase != null)
5139  {
5140  deviceBuilder.DeviceBase.InventoryItemId = inventoryItemId;
5141  }
5142  }
5143  }
5144 
5145  return weaponEntityBuilder;
5146  }

5155  {
5156  m_currentWeapon.EndShoot(action);

5180  public void Use()
5181  {
5182  if (!IsDead)
5183  {
5184  MyCharacterDetectorComponent detectorComponent = Components.Get<MyCharacterDetectorComponent>();
5185 
5186  if (detectorComponent != null && detectorComponent.UseObject != null)
5187  {
5188  if (detectorComponent.UseObject.IsActionSupported(UseActionEnum.Manipulate))
5189  {
5190  if (detectorComponent.UseObject.PlayIndicatorSound)
5191  {
5192  MyGuiAudio.PlaySound(MyGuiSounds.HudUse);
5193  SoundComp.StopStateSound(true);
5194  }
5195  detectorComponent.UseObject.Use(UseActionEnum.Manipulate, this);
5196  }
5197  else if (detectorComponent.UseObject.IsActionSupported(UseActionEnum.OpenTerminal))
5198  {
5199  if (detectorComponent.UseObject.PlayIndicatorSound)
5200  {
5201  MyGuiAudio.PlaySound(MyGuiSounds.HudUse);
5202  SoundComp.StopStateSound(true);
5203  }
5204 
5205  //by Gregory: the parameter that should be passed should be the use key now with flags there can be confusion
5206  //e.g. case for MyUseObjectInventory where it has 2 flags and from use key it should use OpenInventory not OpenTerminal TODO
5207 
5208  detectorComponent.UseObject.Use(UseActionEnum.OpenTerminal, this);
5209  }
5210  else if (detectorComponent.UseObject.IsActionSupported(UseActionEnum.OpenInventory))
5211  {
5212  if (detectorComponent.UseObject.PlayIndicatorSound)
5213  {
5214  MyGuiAudio.PlaySound(MyGuiSounds.HudUse);
5215  SoundComp.StopStateSound(true);
5216  }
5217  detectorComponent.UseObject.Use(UseActionEnum.OpenInventory, this);
5218  }
5219  }
5220  else
5221  {
5222  var detectedEntity = detectorComponent.DetectedEntity as MyEntity;
5223  if (detectedEntity != null && (!(detectedEntity is MyCharacter) || (detectedEntity as MyCharacter).IsDead))
5224  {
5225  MyInventoryBase interactedInventory = null;
5226  if (detectedEntity.TryGetInventory(out interactedInventory))
5227  {
5228  ShowAggregateInventoryScreen(interactedInventory);
5229  }
5230  }
5231  }
5232  }
5233  }

5299  private bool HasEnoughSpaceToStandUp()
5300  {
5301  if (IsCrouching == false)
5302  {
5303  return true;
5304  }
5305 
5306  Vector3D characterHeadPosition = WorldMatrix.Translation + Definition.CharacterCollisionCrouchHeight * WorldMatrix.Up;
5307  float heightDifference = Definition.CharacterCollisionHeight - Definition.CharacterCollisionCrouchHeight;
5308 
5309  Sandbox.Engine.Physics.MyPhysics.HitInfo? hit = MyPhysics.CastRay(characterHeadPosition, characterHeadPosition + heightDifference * WorldMatrix.Up, MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.CharacterCollisionLayer);
5310  if (hit.HasValue)
5311  {
5312  return false;
5313  }
5314 
5315  return true;
5316  }

5326  {
5327  WantsCrouch = !WantsCrouch;

5365  [Event, Reliable, Server]
5366  public void Jump()
5367  {
5368  // Check if not dead.
5369  if (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died)
5370  return;
5371 
5372  if (HasEnoughSpaceToStandUp() == false)
5373  {
5374  return;
5375  }
5376  // Check if can jump. (ex. enough stamina)
5377  MyTuple<ushort, MyStringHash> message;
5378  if (StatComp != null && !StatComp.CanDoAction("Jump", out message, m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump))
5379  {
5380  if (MySession.Static != null && MySession.Static.LocalCharacter == this && message.Item1 == MyStatLogic.STAT_VALUE_TOO_LOW && message.Item2.String.CompareTo("Stamina") == 0)
5381  {
5382  if (m_notEnoughStatNotification != null)
5383  {
5384  m_notEnoughStatNotification.SetTextFormatArguments(message.Item2);
5385  MyHud.Notifications.Add(m_notEnoughStatNotification);
5386  }
5387  }
5388  return;
5389  }
5390 
5391  WantsJump = true;
5392  }

5785  private void OnCharacterStateChanged(HkCharacterStateType newState)
5786  {
5787  if (m_currentMovementState != MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died)
5788  {
5789  if (!JetpackRunning)
5790  {
5791  if (m_currentJumpTime <= 0 && (newState == HkCharacterStateType.HK_CHARACTER_IN_AIR) || ((int)newState == MyCharacter.HK_CHARACTER_FLYING))
5792  {
5793  StartFalling();
5794  }
5795  else
5796  {
5797  if (m_isFalling)
5798  {
5799  StopFalling();
5800  }
5801  }
5802  }
5803 
5804  // Reset jump time in flying mode
5805  if (JetpackRunning)
5806  {
5807  m_currentJumpTime = 0.0f;
5808  }
5809  }
5810 
5811  m_currentCharacterState = newState;
5812 
5813  //MyTrace.Watch("CharacterState", newState.ToString());
5814  }

5816  internal void StartFalling()
5817  {
5818  bool canFly = JetpackRunning;
5819  if (canFly || m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died || m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Sitting)
5820  return;
5821 
5822  if (m_currentCharacterState == HkCharacterStateType.HK_CHARACTER_JUMPING)
5823  {
5824  m_currentFallingTime = -JUMP_TIME;
5825  }
5826  else
5827  m_currentFallingTime = 0;
5828 
5829  m_isFalling = true;
5830  m_crouchAfterFall = WantsCrouch;
5831  WantsCrouch = false;
5832 
5833  SetCurrentMovementState(MyCharacterMovementEnum.Falling);
5834  }
5835 
5836  internal void StopFalling()
5837  {
5838  if (m_currentMovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Died)
5839  return;
5840 
5841  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
5842  if (m_isFalling && (jetpack == null || !(jetpack.TurnedOn && jetpack.IsPowered)))
5843  SoundComp.PlayFallSound();
5844 
5845  if (Physics.CharacterProxy != null)
5846  {
5847  if (m_isFalling)
5848  {
5849  m_movementsFlagsChanged = true;
5850  //PlayCharacterAnimation("Idle", MyBlendOption.Immediate, MyFrameOption.Loop, 0.2f);
5851  //Physics.CharacterProxy.PosX = 0;
5852  //Physics.CharacterProxy.PosY = 0;
5853  //SetCurrentMovementState(MyCharacterMovementEnum.Standing);
5854  }
5855  }
5856 
5857  m_isFalling = false;
5858  m_isFallingAnimationPlayed = false;
5859  m_currentFallingTime = 0;
5860  m_canJump = true;
5861  WantsCrouch = m_crouchAfterFall;
5862  m_crouchAfterFall = false;
5863  }

5869  public bool CanStartConstruction(MyCubeBlockDefinition blockDefinition)
5870  {
5871  if (blockDefinition == null) return false;
5872 
5873  Debug.Assert(this.GetInventory() != null, "Inventory is null!");
5874  Debug.Assert(blockDefinition.Components.Length != 0, "Missing components!");
5875 
5876  var inventory = MyCubeBuilder.BuildComponent.GetBuilderInventory(this);
5877  if (inventory == null)
5878  return false;
5879 
5880  return (inventory.GetItemAmount(blockDefinition.Components[0].Definition.Id) >= 1);
5881  }
5882 
5883  public bool CanStartConstruction(Dictionary<MyDefinitionId, int> constructionCost)
5884  {
5885  Debug.Assert(this.GetInventory() != null, "Inventory is null!");
5886  var inventory = MyCubeBuilder.BuildComponent.GetBuilderInventory(this);
5887  foreach (var entry in constructionCost)
5888  {
5889  if (inventory.GetItemAmount(entry.Key) < entry.Value) return false;
5890  }
5891  return true;
5892  }

5910  [Event, Reliable, Server, BroadcastExcept]
5911  public void UnequipWeapon()
5912  {
5913  if (m_leftHandItem != null && m_leftHandItem is IMyHandheldGunObject<MyDeviceBase>)
5914  {
5915  (m_leftHandItem as IMyHandheldGunObject<MyDeviceBase>).OnControlReleased();
5916  m_leftHandItem.Close(); // no dual wielding now
5917  m_leftHandItem = null;
5918 
5919  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("unequip_left_tool", true);
5920  }
5921 
5922  if (m_currentWeapon != null)
5923  {
5924  //GK: When switching weapon EndShoot unless player is already pressing to shoot
5925  if (!MyInput.Static.IsGameControlPressed(MyControlsSpace.PRIMARY_TOOL_ACTION) && !MyInput.Static.IsGameControlPressed(MyControlsSpace.SECONDARY_TOOL_ACTION))
5926  {
5927  EndShootAll();
5928  }
5929  else if (Sync.IsServer)
5930  {
5931  // prevent player continuing to fire from the unequiped weapon, but keep the shooting flags in character
5932  foreach (MyShootActionEnum action in MyEnum<MyShootActionEnum>.Values)
5933  if (IsShooting(action))
5934  m_currentWeapon.EndShoot(action);
5935  }
5936 
5937  var weaponEntity = m_currentWeapon as MyEntity;
5938  if (UseNewAnimationSystem && m_handItemDefinition != null)
5939  {
5940  if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(m_handItemDefinition.Id.SubtypeName))
5941  {
5942  AnimationController.Variables.SetValue(MyStringId.GetOrCompute(m_handItemDefinition.Id.TypeId.ToString().ToLower()), 0);
5943  }
5944  }
5945 
5946  SaveAmmoToWeapon();
5947 
5948  m_currentWeapon.OnControlReleased();
5949  if (m_zoomMode == MyZoomModeEnum.IronSight && MySession.Static.CameraController == this)
5950  {
5951  bool backupIsInFirstPerson = IsInFirstPersonView;
5952  EnableIronsight(false, true, changeCamera: true);
5953  IsInFirstPersonView = backupIsInFirstPerson;
5954  }
5955 
5956  var weaponSink = weaponEntity.Components.Get<MyResourceSinkComponent>();
5957  if (weaponSink != null)
5958  SuitRechargeDistributor.RemoveSink(weaponSink);
5959 
5960  weaponEntity.OnClose -= gunEntity_OnClose;
5961 
5962  MyEntities.Remove(weaponEntity);
5963 
5964  weaponEntity.Close();
5965  //var useAnimationInsteadOfIK = MyPerGameSettings.CheckUseAnimationInsteadOfIK(m_currentWeapon);
5966 
5967  m_currentWeapon = null;
5968 
5969  if (ControllerInfo.IsLocallyHumanControlled() && MySector.MainCamera != null)
5970  {
5971  MySector.MainCamera.Zoom.ResetZoom();
5972  }
5973 
5974  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
5975  {
5976  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("unequip_left_tool", true);
5977  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("unequip_right_tool", true);
5978  }
5979  else
5980  {
5981  StopUpperAnimation(0.2f);
5982  SwitchAnimation(m_currentMovementState, false);
5983  }
5984 
5985  MyAnalyticsHelper.ReportActivityEnd(this, "item_equip");
5986  }
5987 
5988  if (m_currentShotTime <= 0)
5989  {
5990  //Otherwise all upper players keep updating
5991  StopUpperAnimation(0);
5992  StopFingersAnimation(0);
5993  }
5994 
5995  //MyHud.Crosshair.Hide();
5996  m_currentWeapon = null;
5997  StopFingersAnimation(0);
5998  }

6000  private void EquipWeapon(IMyHandheldGunObject<MyDeviceBase> newWeapon, bool showNotification = false)
6001  {
6002  // Debug.Assert(newWeapon != null);
6003  if (newWeapon == null)
6004  return;
6005 
6006  MyEntity gunEntity = (MyEntity)newWeapon;
6007  gunEntity.Render.CastShadows = true;
6008  gunEntity.Render.NeedsResolveCastShadow = false;
6009  gunEntity.Save = false;
6010  gunEntity.OnClose += gunEntity_OnClose;
6011 
6012  MyEntities.Add(gunEntity);
6013 
6014  m_handItemDefinition = null;
6015  m_currentWeapon = newWeapon;
6016  m_currentWeapon.OnControlAcquired(this);
6017 
6018  if (WeaponEquiped != null)
6019  WeaponEquiped(m_currentWeapon);
6020 
6021  MyAnalyticsHelper.ReportActivityStart(this, "item_equip", "character", "toolbar_item_usage", m_currentWeapon.GetType().Name);
6022 
6023  // CH:TODO: The hand item definitions should be changed to handheld gun object definitions and should be taken according to m_currentWeapon typeId
6024  if (m_currentWeapon.PhysicalObject != null)
6025  {
6026  var handItemId = m_currentWeapon.PhysicalObject.GetId();
6027 
6028  m_handItemDefinition = MyDefinitionManager.Static.TryGetHandItemForPhysicalItem(handItemId);
6029  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(m_handItemDefinition != null, "Create definition for this hand item!");
6030  }
6031  else if (m_currentWeapon.DefinitionId.TypeId == typeof(MyObjectBuilder_CubePlacer))
6032  {
6033  var gunID = new MyDefinitionId(typeof(MyObjectBuilder_CubePlacer));
6034 
6035  m_handItemDefinition = MyDefinitionManager.Static.TryGetHandItemDefinition(ref gunID);
6036  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(m_handItemDefinition != null, "Create definition for this hand item!");
6037  }
6038 
6039  //Setup correct worldmatrix to weapon
6040  //CalculateDependentMatrices();
6041 
6042  if (m_handItemDefinition != null && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(m_handItemDefinition.FingersAnimation))
6043  {
6044  string animationSubtype;
6045  if (!m_characterDefinition.AnimationNameToSubtypeName.TryGetValue(m_handItemDefinition.FingersAnimation, out animationSubtype))
6046  {
6047  animationSubtype = m_handItemDefinition.FingersAnimation;
6048  }
6049  var def = MyDefinitionManager.Static.TryGetAnimationDefinition(animationSubtype);
6050  if (!def.LeftHandItem.TypeId.IsNull)
6051  {
6052  m_currentWeapon.OnControlReleased();
6053  (m_currentWeapon as MyEntity).Close(); //no dual wielding now
6054  m_currentWeapon = null;
6055  }
6056 
6057  PlayCharacterAnimation(m_handItemDefinition.FingersAnimation, MyBlendOption.Immediate, def.Loop ? MyFrameOption.Loop : MyFrameOption.PlayOnce, 1.0f, 1, false, null);
6058  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
6059  {
6060  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("equip_left_tool", true);
6061  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("equip_right_tool", true);
6062  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent(m_handItemDefinition.Id.SubtypeName.ToLower(), true);
6063  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent(m_handItemDefinition.FingersAnimation.ToLower(), true);
6064 
6065  if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(m_handItemDefinition.Id.SubtypeName))
6066  {
6067  AnimationController.Variables.SetValue(MyStringId.GetOrCompute(m_handItemDefinition.Id.TypeId.ToString().ToLower()), 1);
6068  }
6069  }
6070 
6071  if (!def.LeftHandItem.TypeId.IsNull)
6072  {
6073  if (m_leftHandItem != null)
6074  {
6075  (m_leftHandItem as IMyHandheldGunObject<Sandbox.Game.Weapons.MyDeviceBase>).OnControlReleased();
6076  m_leftHandItem.Close();
6077  }
6078 
6079  // CH: TODO: The entity id is not synced, but it never was in this place. It should be fixed later
6080  long handItemId = MyEntityIdentifier.AllocateId();
6081  uint? inventoryItemId = null;
6082  var builder = GetObjectBuilderForWeapon(def.LeftHandItem, ref inventoryItemId, handItemId);
6083  var leftHandItem = CreateGun(builder, inventoryItemId);
6084 
6085  if (leftHandItem != null)
6086  {
6087  m_leftHandItem = leftHandItem as MyEntity;
6088  leftHandItem.OnControlAcquired(this);
6089  UpdateLeftHandItemPosition();
6090 
6091  MyEntities.Add(m_leftHandItem);
6092  }
6093  }
6094  }
6095  else if (m_handItemDefinition != null)
6096  {
6097  if (UseNewAnimationSystem)
6098  {
6099  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("equip_left_tool", true);
6100  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("equip_right_tool", true);
6101  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent(m_handItemDefinition.Id.SubtypeName.ToLower(), true);
6102  }
6103  }
6104  else
6105  {
6106  StopFingersAnimation(0);
6107  }
6108 
6109  var consumer = gunEntity.Components.Get<MyResourceSinkComponent>();
6110  if (consumer != null && SuitRechargeDistributor != null)
6111  SuitRechargeDistributor.AddSink(consumer);
6112 
6113  if (showNotification)
6114  {
6115  var notificationUse = new MyHudNotification(MySpaceTexts.NotificationUsingWeaponType, 2000);
6116  notificationUse.SetTextFormatArguments(MyDeviceBase.GetGunNotificationName(newWeapon.DefinitionId));
6117  MyHud.Notifications.Add(notificationUse);
6118  }
6119 
6120  Static_CameraAttachedToChanged(null, null);
6121  if (!(IsUsing is MyCockpit))
6122  MyHud.Crosshair.ResetToDefault(clear: false);
6123  }

6367 
6368  public bool DoDamage(float damage, MyStringHash damageType, bool updateSync, long attackerId = 0)
6369  {
6370  damage *= CharacterGeneralDamageModifier;
6371  if (damage < 0)
6372  return false;
6373 
6374  if (damageType != MyDamageType.Suicide && ControllerInfo.IsLocallyControlled()
6375  && MySession.Static.CameraController == this)
6376  {
6377  const float maxShake = 5.0f;
6378  MySector.MainCamera.CameraShake.AddShake(maxShake * damage / (damage + maxShake));
6379  }
6380 
6381  if ((!CharacterCanDie && !(damageType == MyDamageType.Suicide && MyPerGameSettings.CharacterSuicideEnabled)) || StatComp == null)
6382  return false;
6383 
6384  if (MySession.Static.AdminSettings.HasFlag(AdminSettingsEnum.Invulnerable))
6385  return false;
6386  else if (ControllerInfo.Controller != null && ControllerInfo.Controller.Player != null)
6387  {
6388  AdminSettingsEnum set;
6389  if (MySession.Static.RemoteAdminSettings.TryGetValue(ControllerInfo.Controller.Player.Id.SteamId, out set))
6390  {
6391  if (set.HasFlag(AdminSettingsEnum.Invulnerable))
6392  return false;
6393  }
6394  }
6395 
6396  MyEntity attacker;
6397  if (damageType != MyDamageType.Suicide && MyEntities.TryGetEntityById(attackerId, out attacker))
6398  { // Checking friendly fire using faction's friendly fire settings
6399  var localPlayer = MyPlayer.GetPlayerFromCharacter(this);
6400  MyPlayer otherPlayer = null;
6401  if (attacker == this)
6402  {
6403  return false;
6404  }
6405  else if (attacker is MyCharacter)
6406  {
6407  otherPlayer = MyPlayer.GetPlayerFromCharacter(attacker as MyCharacter);
6408  }
6409  else if (attacker is IMyGunBaseUser)
6410  {
6411  otherPlayer = MyPlayer.GetPlayerFromWeapon(attacker as IMyGunBaseUser);
6412  }
6413  else if (attacker is MyHandDrill)
6414  {
6415  otherPlayer = MyPlayer.GetPlayerFromCharacter((attacker as MyHandDrill).Owner);
6416  }
6417 
6418  if (localPlayer != null && otherPlayer != null)
6419  {
6420  var localPlayerFaction = MySession.Static.Factions.TryGetPlayerFaction(localPlayer.Identity.IdentityId) as MyFaction;
6421  if (localPlayerFaction != null && !localPlayerFaction.EnableFriendlyFire && localPlayerFaction.IsMember(otherPlayer.Identity.IdentityId))
6422  {
6423  return false; // No Friendly Fire Enabled!
6424  }
6425  }
6426 
6427  if (damage >= 0f && MySession.Static != null && MyMusicController.Static != null)
6428  {
6429  if (this == MySession.Static.LocalCharacter && attacker is MyVoxelPhysics == false && attacker is MyCubeGrid == false)
6430  MyMusicController.Static.Fighting(false, (int)damage * 3);//not fall damage
6431  else if (attacker == MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
6432  MyMusicController.Static.Fighting(false, (int)damage * 2);//attack other character
6433  else if (attacker is IMyGunBaseUser && (attacker as IMyGunBaseUser).Owner as MyCharacter == MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
6434  MyMusicController.Static.Fighting(false, (int)damage * 2);//attack other character with gun
6435  else if (MySession.Static.ControlledEntity == attacker)
6436  MyMusicController.Static.Fighting(false, (int)damage);//attack other character with turret
6437  }
6438  }
6439 
6440  MyDamageInformation damageInfo = new MyDamageInformation(false, damage, damageType, attackerId);
6441  if (UseDamageSystem && !(m_dieAfterSimulation || IsDead))
6442  MyDamageSystem.Static.RaiseBeforeDamageApplied(this, ref damageInfo);
6443 
6444  if (damageInfo.Amount <= 0f)
6445  return false;
6446 
6447  StatComp.DoDamage(damage, updateSync, damageInfo);
6448 
6449  // Cache the last damage information for the analytics module.
6450  MyAnalyticsHelper.SetLastDamageInformation(damageInfo);
6451 
6452  if (UseDamageSystem)
6453  MyDamageSystem.Static.RaiseAfterDamageApplied(this, damageInfo);
6454 
6455  if (updateSync)
6456  TriggerCharacterAnimationEvent("hurt", true);
6457  else
6458  AnimationController.TriggerAction(MyAnimationVariableStorageHints.StrIdActionHurt);
6459 
6460  return true;
6461  }
6462 
6463  void IMyDecalProxy.AddDecals(MyHitInfo hitInfo, MyStringHash source, object customdata, IMyDecalHandler decalHandler, MyStringHash material)
6464  {
6465  MyCharacterHitInfo charHitInfo = customdata as MyCharacterHitInfo;
6466  if (charHitInfo == null || charHitInfo.BoneIndex == -1)
6467  return;
6468 
6469  MyDecalRenderInfo renderable = new MyDecalRenderInfo();
6470  renderable.Position = charHitInfo.Triangle.IntersectionPointInObjectSpace;
6471  renderable.Normal = charHitInfo.Triangle.NormalInObjectSpace;
6472  renderable.RenderObjectId = Render.GetRenderObjectID();
6473 
6474  if (material.GetHashCode() == 0)
6475  renderable.Material = MyStringHash.GetOrCompute(m_characterDefinition.PhysicalMaterial);
6476  else
6477  renderable.Material = material;
6478 
6479 
6480  VertexBoneIndicesWeights? boneIndicesWeights = charHitInfo.Triangle.GetAffectingBoneIndicesWeights(ref m_boneIndexWeightTmp);
6481  renderable.BoneIndices = boneIndicesWeights.Value.Indices;
6482  renderable.BoneWeights = boneIndicesWeights.Value.Weights;
6483 
6484  renderable.Binding = new MyDecalBindingInfo()
6485  {
6486  Position = charHitInfo.HitPositionBindingPose,
6487  Normal = charHitInfo.HitNormalBindingPose,
6488  Transformation = charHitInfo.BindingTransformation
6489  };
6490 
6491  var decalId = decalHandler.AddDecal(ref renderable);
6492  if (decalId == null)
6493  return;
6494 
6495  AddBoneDecal(decalId.Value, charHitInfo.BoneIndex);
6496  }

6512  public void Kill(bool sync, MyDamageInformation damageInfo)
6513  {
6514  if (m_dieAfterSimulation || IsDead || (MyFakes.DEVELOPMENT_PRESET && damageInfo.Type != MyDamageType.Suicide))
6515  return;
6516 
6517  if (sync)
6518  {
6519  KillCharacter(damageInfo);
6520  return;
6521  }
6522 
6523  if (UseDamageSystem)
6524  MyDamageSystem.Static.RaiseDestroyed(this, damageInfo);
6525 
6526  MyAnalyticsHelper.SetLastDamageInformation(damageInfo);
6527 
6528  m_dieAfterSimulation = true;
6529  }

6549  {

6551  return;

6629  {

6632  turret.ForceReleaseControl();
6633  }

6636  {

6640 
6641  ulong playerId = 0;

6680  else
6681  {
6682  deathLocation = new MyGps();

6685  deathLocation.Coords = new Vector3D(MySession.Static.LocalHumanPlayer.GetPosition());

6763  private void StartRespawn(float respawnTime)
6764  {
6765  if (ControllerInfo.Controller != null && ControllerInfo.Controller.Player != null)
6766  {

6769  MyVisualScriptLogicProvider.PlayerDied(ControllerInfo.Controller.Player.Identity.IdentityId);
6770  if (MyVisualScriptLogicProvider.NPCDied != null && IsBot)
6771  MyVisualScriptLogicProvider.NPCDied(DefinitionId.HasValue ? DefinitionId.Value.SubtypeName : "");
6772  if (!MySessionComponentMissionTriggers.CanRespawn(this.ControllerInfo.Controller.Player.Id))
6773  {
6774  m_currentRespawnCounter = -1;
6775  return;
6776  }
6777  }
6778 
6779  if (this == MySession.Static.ControlledEntity)
6780  {
6781  MyGuiScreenTerminal.Hide();
6782 
6783  m_respawnNotification = new MyHudNotification(MyCommonTexts.NotificationRespawn, (int)(RESPAWN_TIME * 1000), priority: 5);
6784  m_respawnNotification.Level = MyNotificationLevel.Important;
6785  m_respawnNotification.SetTextFormatArguments((int)m_currentRespawnCounter);
6786  MyHud.Notifications.Add(m_respawnNotification);
6787  }
6788 
6789  m_currentRespawnCounter = respawnTime;
6790 
6791  NeedsUpdate |= MyEntityUpdateEnum.EACH_FRAME;
6792  }

6794  private void InitDeadBodyPhysics()
6795  {
6796  Vector3 velocity = Vector3.Zero;
6797 
6798  RadioBroadcaster.BroadcastRadius = 5;
6799 
6800  if (Physics != null)
6801  {
6802  velocity = Physics.LinearVelocity;
6803 
6804  Physics.Enabled = false;
6805  Physics.Close();
6806  Physics = null;
6807  }
6808 
6809  //if (Physics == null)
6810  {
6811  var massProperties = new HkMassProperties();
6812  massProperties.Mass = 500;
6813 
6814  HkShape shape;
6815  // CH: Need to rethink this. It does not belong here, but I don't want to add "DeadCharacterBodyCenterOfMass" to the character definition either...
6816  // MZ: See ticket "Correct dying for characters", https://app.asana.com/0/64822442925263/75411538582998
6817  // dead body shape can now be specified in character's SBC
6818  if (Definition.DeadBodyShape != null)
6819  {
6820  HkBoxShape bshape = new HkBoxShape(PositionComp.LocalAABB.HalfExtents * Definition.DeadBodyShape.BoxShapeScale);
6821  massProperties = HkInertiaTensorComputer.ComputeBoxVolumeMassProperties(bshape.HalfExtents, massProperties.Mass);
6822  massProperties.CenterOfMass = bshape.HalfExtents * Definition.DeadBodyShape.RelativeCenterOfMass;
6823  shape = bshape;
6824 
6825  Physics = new MyPhysicsBody(this, RigidBodyFlag.RBF_DEFAULT);
6826  Vector3D offset = PositionComp.LocalAABB.HalfExtents * Definition.DeadBodyShape.RelativeShapeTranslation;
6827  MatrixD pos = MatrixD.CreateTranslation(offset);
6828  Physics.CreateFromCollisionObject(shape, PositionComp.LocalVolume.Center + offset, pos, massProperties, MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.FloatingObjectCollisionLayer);
6829  Physics.Friction = Definition.DeadBodyShape.Friction;
6830  Physics.RigidBody.MaxAngularVelocity = MathHelper.PiOver2;
6831  Physics.LinearVelocity = velocity;
6832  shape.RemoveReference();
6833 
6834  Physics.Enabled = true;
6835  }
6836  else // no special definition => use AABB
6837  {
6838  HkBoxShape bshape = new HkBoxShape(PositionComp.LocalAABB.HalfExtents);
6839  massProperties = HkInertiaTensorComputer.ComputeBoxVolumeMassProperties(bshape.HalfExtents, massProperties.Mass);
6840  massProperties.CenterOfMass = new Vector3(bshape.HalfExtents.X, 0, 0);
6841  shape = bshape;
6842 
6843  Physics = new MyPhysicsBody(this, RigidBodyFlag.RBF_DEFAULT);
6844  //<ib.ragdoll> VRAG-106 Fix ragdoll bone transformations, Center must be zero for ragdoll
6845  //Physics.CreateFromCollisionObject(shape, PositionComp.LocalVolume.Center, MatrixD.Identity, massProperties, MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.FloatingObjectCollisionLayer);
6846  Physics.CreateFromCollisionObject(shape, Vector3.Zero, MatrixD.Identity, massProperties, MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.FloatingObjectCollisionLayer);
6847  Physics.Friction = 0.5f;
6848  Physics.RigidBody.MaxAngularVelocity = MathHelper.PiOver2;
6849  Physics.LinearVelocity = velocity;
6850  shape.RemoveReference();
6851 
6852  Physics.Enabled = true;
6853  }
6854  }
6855 
6856  NeedsUpdate |= MyEntityUpdateEnum.BEFORE_NEXT_FRAME;
6857  }

6877  }

6881  if (m_currentWeapon != null)

6894  //MySpectatorCameraController.Static.Position = this.PositionComp.GetPosition();
6895  }

6958  public void SetLocalHeadAnimation(float? targetX, float? targetY, float length)
6959  {
6960  if (length > 0)
6961  {
6962  // prevent rotating back many loops -> limit y rot to -180.0f,+180.0f
6963  if (m_headLocalYAngle < 0)
6964  {
6965  m_headLocalYAngle = -m_headLocalYAngle;
6966  m_headLocalYAngle = (m_headLocalYAngle + 180.0f) % 360.0f - 180.0f;
6967  m_headLocalYAngle = -m_headLocalYAngle;
6968  }
6969  else
6970  {
6971  m_headLocalYAngle = (m_headLocalYAngle + 180.0f) % 360.0f - 180.0f;
6972  }
6973  }
6974  m_currentLocalHeadAnimation = 0;
6975  m_localHeadAnimationLength = length;
6976  if (targetX.HasValue)
6977  m_localHeadAnimationX = new Vector2(m_headLocalXAngle, targetX.Value);
6978  else
6979  m_localHeadAnimationX = null;
6980 
6981  if (targetY.HasValue)
6982  m_localHeadAnimationY = new Vector2(m_headLocalYAngle, targetY.Value);
6983  else
6984  m_localHeadAnimationY = null;
6985  }

6988  {
6989  return m_currentLocalHeadAnimation >= 0;
6990  }

7016  public static MyCharacter CreateCharacter(MatrixD worldMatrix, Vector3 velocity, string characterName, string model, Vector3? colorMask, MyBotDefinition botDefinition, bool findNearPos = true, bool AIMode = false, MyCockpit cockpit = null, bool useInventory = true, ulong playerSteamId = 0)
7017  {
7018  Vector3D? characterPos = null;
7019  if (findNearPos)
7020  {
7021  characterPos = MyEntities.FindFreePlace(worldMatrix.Translation, 2, 200, 5, 0.5f);
7022 
7023  // Extended search
7024  if (!characterPos.HasValue)
7025  {
7026  characterPos = MyEntities.FindFreePlace(worldMatrix.Translation, 2, 200, 5, 5);
7027  }
7028  }
7029 
7030  // Use default position
7031  if (characterPos.HasValue)
7032  {
7033  worldMatrix.Translation = characterPos.Value;
7034  }
7035 
7036  MyCharacter character = CreateCharacterBase(worldMatrix, ref velocity, characterName, model, colorMask, AIMode, useInventory, botDefinition);
7037 
7038  if (cockpit == null && Sync.IsServer && MyPerGameSettings.BlockForVoxels == false)
7039  {
7040  MyMultiplayer.ReplicateImmediatelly(MyExternalReplicable.FindByObject(character), new EndpointId(playerSteamId));
7041  }
7042  return character;
7043  }
7044 
7045  private static MyCharacter CreateCharacterBase(MatrixD worldMatrix, ref Vector3 velocity, string characterName, string model, Vector3? colorMask, bool AIMode, bool useInventory = true, MyBotDefinition botDefinition = null)
7046  {
7047  MyCharacter character = new MyCharacter();
7048  MyObjectBuilder_Character objectBuilder = MyCharacter.Random();
7049  objectBuilder.CharacterModel = model ?? objectBuilder.CharacterModel;
7050 
7051  if (colorMask.HasValue)
7052  objectBuilder.ColorMaskHSV = colorMask.Value;
7053 
7054  objectBuilder.JetpackEnabled = MySession.Static.CreativeMode;
7055  objectBuilder.Battery = new MyObjectBuilder_Battery { CurrentCapacity = 1 };
7056  objectBuilder.AIMode = AIMode;
7057  objectBuilder.DisplayName = characterName;
7058  objectBuilder.LinearVelocity = velocity;
7059  objectBuilder.PositionAndOrientation = new MyPositionAndOrientation(worldMatrix);
7060  objectBuilder.CharacterGeneralDamageModifier = 1f;
7061  character.Init(objectBuilder);
7062 
7063  MyEntities.RaiseEntityCreated(character);
7064  MyEntities.Add(character);
7065 
7066  character.IsReadyForReplication = true;
7067 
7068  System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(character.GetInventory() as MyInventory != null, "Null or unexpected inventory type returned!");
7069  if (useInventory)
7070  MyWorldGenerator.InitInventoryWithDefaults(character.GetInventory() as MyInventory);
7071  else if (botDefinition != null)
7072  {
7073  // use inventory from bot definition
7074  botDefinition.AddItems(character);
7075  }
7076  //character.PositionComp.SetWorldMatrix(worldMatrix);
7077  if (velocity.Length() > 0)
7078  {
7079  var jetpack = character.JetpackComp;
7080 
7081  if (jetpack != null)
7082  jetpack.EnableDampeners(false, false);
7083  }
7084 
7085  return character;
7086  }

7127  public void UpdateHudCharacterInfo()
7128  {
7129  MyHud.CharacterInfo.BatteryEnergy = 100 * SuitBattery.ResourceSource.RemainingCapacityByType(MyResourceDistributorComponent.ElectricityId) / MyEnergyConstants.BATTERY_MAX_CAPACITY;
7130  MyHud.CharacterInfo.IsBatteryEnergyLow = SuitBattery.IsEnergyLow;
7131  MyHud.CharacterInfo.Speed = Physics.LinearVelocity.Length();
7132  MyHud.CharacterInfo.Mass = this.GetInventory() != null ? (int)((float)this.GetInventory().CurrentMass + Definition.Mass) : 0;
7133  MyHud.CharacterInfo.LightEnabled = LightEnabled;
7134  MyHud.CharacterInfo.BroadcastEnabled = RadioBroadcaster.Enabled;
7135 
7136  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
7137  bool canFly = JetpackRunning;
7138  MyHud.CharacterInfo.DampenersEnabled = jetpack != null && jetpack.DampenersTurnedOn;
7139  MyHud.CharacterInfo.JetpackEnabled = jetpack != null && jetpack.TurnedOn;
7140 
7141  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Standing;
7142  var entity = MySession.Static.ControlledEntity;
7143  var cockpit = entity as MyCockpit;
7144  if (entity != null)
7145  {
7146  if (cockpit != null)
7147  {
7148  var grid = cockpit.CubeGrid;
7149  if (grid.GridSizeEnum == MyCubeSize.Small)
7150  {
7151  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.PilotingSmallShip;
7152  }
7153  else
7154  {
7155  if (grid.IsStatic)
7156  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.ControllingStation;
7157  else
7158  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.PilotingLargeShip;
7159  }
7160  }
7161  else
7162  {
7163  if (canFly)
7164  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Flying;
7165  else
7166  if (IsMagneticBootsEnabled)
7167  {
7168  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Magnetic;
7169  }
7170  else
7171  if (IsCrouching)
7172  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Crouching;
7173  else
7174  if (IsFalling)
7175  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Falling;
7176  else
7177  MyHud.CharacterInfo.State = MyHudCharacterStateEnum.Standing;
7178  }
7179  }
7180 
7181  float healthRatio = 1.0f;
7182  if (StatComp != null)
7183  healthRatio = StatComp.HealthRatio;
7184 
7185  MyHud.CharacterInfo.HealthRatio = healthRatio;
7186  MyHud.CharacterInfo.IsHealthLow = healthRatio < MyCharacterStatComponent.LOW_HEALTH_RATIO;
7187  MyHud.CharacterInfo.InventoryVolume = this.GetInventory() != null ? this.GetInventory().CurrentVolume : 0;
7188  MyHud.CharacterInfo.IsInventoryFull = this.GetInventory() == null || ((float)this.GetInventory().CurrentVolume / (float)this.GetInventory().MaxVolume) > 0.95f;
7189  MyHud.CharacterInfo.BroadcastRange = RadioBroadcaster.BroadcastRadius;
7190  if (OxygenComponent != null)
7191  {
7192  MyHud.CharacterInfo.OxygenLevel = OxygenComponent.SuitOxygenLevel;
7193  MyHud.CharacterInfo.HydrogenRatio = OxygenComponent.GetGasFillLevel(MyCharacterOxygenComponent.HydrogenId);
7194  MyHud.CharacterInfo.IsOxygenLevelLow = OxygenComponent.IsOxygenLevelLow;
7195  MyHud.CharacterInfo.IsHelmetOn = OxygenComponent.HelmetEnabled;
7196  }
7197  }
7198 
7199  internal void UpdateCharacterPhysics(bool isLocalPlayer)
7200  {
7201  if (Physics != null && Physics.Enabled == false)
7202  return;
7203 
7204  float offset = 2 * MyPerGameSettings.PhysicsConvexRadius + 0.03f; //compensation for convex radius
7205 
7206  float maxSpeedRelativeToShip = Math.Max(Definition.MaxSprintSpeed, Math.Max(Definition.MaxRunSpeed, Definition.MaxBackrunSpeed));
7207 
7208  if (isLocalPlayer || !MyPerGameSettings.EnableKinematicMPCharacter)
7209  {
7210  if (Physics == null || Physics.IsKinematic)
7211  {
7212  if (Physics != null)
7213  Physics.Close();
7214 
7215  this.InitCharacterPhysics(MyMaterialType.CHARACTER, PositionComp.LocalVolume.Center, Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale, Definition.CharacterCollisionHeight - Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale - offset,
7216  Definition.CharacterCollisionCrouchHeight - Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth,
7217  Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth - offset,
7218  Definition.CharacterHeadSize * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale,
7219  Definition.CharacterHeadHeight,
7220  0.7f, 0.7f, (ushort)MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.CharacterCollisionLayer, RigidBodyFlag.RBF_DEFAULT,
7221  MyPerGameSettings.Destruction ? MyDestructionHelper.MassToHavok(Definition.Mass) : Definition.Mass,
7222  Definition.VerticalPositionFlyingOnly,
7223  Definition.MaxSlope,
7224  Definition.ImpulseLimit,
7225  maxSpeedRelativeToShip,
7226  false,
7227  Definition.MaxForce);
7228 
7229  Physics.Enabled = true;
7230  }
7231  }
7232  else
7233  {
7234  if (Physics == null || !Physics.IsKinematic)
7235  {
7236  if (Physics != null)
7237  Physics.Close();
7238 
7239  float scale = Sync.IsServer ? MyPerGameSettings.NetworkCharacterScale : 1;
7240  int layer = Sync.IsServer ? MyPhysics.CollisionLayers.CharacterNetworkCollisionLayer : MyPerGameSettings.NetworkCharacterCollisionLayer;
7241 
7242  this.InitCharacterPhysics(MyMaterialType.CHARACTER, PositionComp.LocalVolume.Center, Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale * scale, Definition.CharacterCollisionHeight - Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale * scale - offset,
7243  Definition.CharacterCollisionCrouchHeight - Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth,
7244  Definition.CharacterCollisionWidth - offset,
7245  Definition.CharacterHeadSize * Definition.CharacterCollisionScale * scale,
7246  Definition.CharacterHeadHeight,
7247  0.7f, 0.7f, (ushort)layer, MyPerGameSettings.NetworkCharacterType, 0, //Mass is not scaled on purpose (collision over networks)
7248  Definition.VerticalPositionFlyingOnly,
7249  Definition.MaxSlope,
7250  Definition.ImpulseLimit,
7251  maxSpeedRelativeToShip,
7252  true,
7253  Definition.MaxForce);
7254 
7255  if (MyPerGameSettings.NetworkCharacterType == RigidBodyFlag.RBF_DEFAULT)
7256  {
7257  Physics.Friction = 1; //to not move on steep surfaces
7258  }
7259 
7260  Physics.Enabled = true;
7261  }
7262  }
7263  }

7267  public void GetNetState(out MyCharacterNetState state)
7268  {
7269  state.HeadX = HeadLocalXAngle;
7270  state.HeadY = HeadLocalYAngle; // 2B
7271  state.MovementState = GetCurrentMovementState();
7272  state.MovementFlags = MovementFlags;
7273  bool hasJetpack = JetpackComp != null;
7274  state.Jetpack = hasJetpack && JetpackComp.TurnedOn;
7275  state.Dampeners = hasJetpack && JetpackComp.DampenersTurnedOn;
7276  state.TargetFromCamera = TargetFromCamera;
7277  state.MoveIndicator = MoveIndicator;
7278  var q = Quaternion.CreateFromRotationMatrix(Entity.WorldMatrix);
7279  state.Rotation = q;
7280  state.Valid = true;
7281  }
7282 
7283  public void SetNetState(ref MyCharacterNetState state, bool animating)
7284  {
7285  if (IsDead || IsUsing != null || Closed)
7286  return;
7287 
7288  SetHeadLocalXAngle(state.HeadX);
7289  SetHeadLocalYAngle(state.HeadY);
7290 
7291  if (!Sandbox.Engine.Utils.MyFakes.MULTIPLAYER_CLIENT_PHYSICS)
7292  m_isFalling = false;
7293 
7294  var jetpack = JetpackComp;
7295  if (jetpack != null)
7296  {
7297  if (state.Jetpack != JetpackComp.TurnedOn)
7298  {
7299  jetpack.TurnOnJetpack(state.Jetpack, true);
7300  }
7301  if (state.Dampeners != JetpackComp.DampenersTurnedOn)
7302  {
7303  jetpack.EnableDampeners(state.Dampeners, false);
7304  }
7305  }
7306  TargetFromCamera = state.TargetFromCamera;
7307 
7308  if (animating)
7309  {
7310  // do it fast, dont wait for update, no time.
7311  UpdateMovementAndFlags(state.MovementState, state.MovementFlags);
7312  if (state.MovementState == MyCharacterMovementEnum.Jump)
7313  {
7314  // Simulate one frame for jump action to be triggered
7315  Jump();
7316  MoveAndRotateInternal(MoveIndicator, RotationIndicator, RollIndicator, Vector3.Zero);
7317  }
7318  }
7319  else
7320  {
7321  // Set client movement state directly and don't perform other operations
7322  // that may have side-effects to let server side Character.UpdateAfterSimulation()
7323  // perform exactly same operations as on client
7324  // Add operator becuase of jump, which can be set on server locally and thus cannot be overriden by late state from client
7325  MovementFlags = state.MovementFlags | (MovementFlags & MyCharacterMovementFlags.Jump);
7326 
7327  if (Sync.IsServer || MyFakes.MULTIPLAYER_SIMULATE_CHARACTER_CLIENT)
7328  {
7329  CacheMove(ref state.MoveIndicator, ref state.Rotation);
7330  }
7331  }
7332  }

7371  private void UpdateLeftHandItemPosition()
7372  {
7373  MatrixD leftHandItemMatrix = AnimationController.CharacterBones[m_leftHandItemBone].AbsoluteTransform * WorldMatrix;
7374  Vector3D up = leftHandItemMatrix.Up;
7375  leftHandItemMatrix.Up = leftHandItemMatrix.Forward;
7376  leftHandItemMatrix.Forward = up;
7377  leftHandItemMatrix.Right = Vector3D.Cross(leftHandItemMatrix.Forward, leftHandItemMatrix.Up);
7378  m_leftHandItem.WorldMatrix = leftHandItemMatrix;
7379  }

7465  internal void ChangeModelAndColorInternal(string model, Vector3 colorMaskHSV)
7466  {
7467  MyCharacterDefinition def;
7468  if (model != m_characterModel && MyDefinitionManager.Static.Characters.TryGetValue(model, out def) && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(def.Model))
7469  {
7470  MyObjectBuilder_Character characterOb = (MyObjectBuilder_Character)GetObjectBuilder();
7471 
7472  var inventory = Components.Get<MyInventoryBase>();
7473  Components.Remove<MyInventoryBase>();
7474  Components.Remove<MyCharacterJetpackComponent>();
7475  Components.Remove<MyCharacterRagdollComponent>();
7476  AnimationController.Clear();
7477 
7478  var newModel = VRage.Game.Models.MyModels.GetModelOnlyData(def.Model);
7479 
7480  if (newModel == null)
7481  return;
7482 
7483  Render.CleanLights();
7484  CloseInternal();
7485 
7486  MyEntities.Remove(this);
7487  Physics.Close();
7488  Physics = null;
7489 
7490  m_characterModel = model;
7491  Render.ModelStorage = newModel;
7492 
7493  characterOb.CharacterModel = model;
7494  characterOb.EntityId = 0;
7495  if (characterOb.HandWeapon != null)
7496  characterOb.HandWeapon.EntityId = 0;
7497 
7498  if (m_breath != null)
7499  {
7500  m_breath.Close();
7501  m_breath = null;
7502  }
7503 
7504  float oldHealthRatio = StatComp != null ? StatComp.HealthRatio : 1f;
7505  float oldHeadLocalX = m_headLocalXAngle;
7506  float oldHeadLocalY = m_headLocalYAngle;
7507 
7508  Init(characterOb);
7509  //GR: Do this in order to reset to max volume and then be able to reinitialize inventory's max volume. Do this only when model is to be changed
7510  this.GetInventory().ResetVolume();
7511  InitInventory(characterOb);
7512 
7513  m_headLocalXAngle = oldHeadLocalX;
7514  m_headLocalYAngle = oldHeadLocalY;
7515 
7516  if (StatComp != null && StatComp.Health != null)
7517  StatComp.Health.Value = StatComp.Health.MaxValue - StatComp.Health.MaxValue * (1f - oldHealthRatio);
7518 
7519  SwitchAnimation(characterOb.MovementState, false);
7520 
7521  if (m_currentWeapon != null)
7522  {
7523  m_currentWeapon.OnControlAcquired(this);
7524  }
7525 
7526  MyEntities.Add(this);
7527 
7528  MyEntityIdentifier.AllocationSuspended = false;
7529 
7530  if (ControllerInfo.Controller != null && ControllerInfo.Controller.Player != null)
7531  {
7532  ControllerInfo.Controller.Player.Identity.ChangeCharacter(this);
7533  }
7534 
7535  // Recharge you suit because is brand new after helmet takin out! (Otherwise you will fall for a moment)
7536  SuitRechargeDistributor.UpdateBeforeSimulation();
7537  }
7538 
7539  Render.ColorMaskHsv = colorMaskHSV;
7540  }

7587  MatrixD IMyUseObject.ActivationMatrix
7588  {
7589  get
7590  {
7591  if (PositionComp == null)
7592  return MatrixD.Zero;
7593 
7594  if (IsDead && Physics != null && Definition.DeadBodyShape != null)
7595  {
7596  float scale = 0.8f;
7597  Matrix m = WorldMatrix;
7598  m.Forward *= scale;
7599  m.Up *= Definition.CharacterCollisionHeight * scale;
7600  m.Right *= scale;
7601  m.Translation = PositionComp.WorldAABB.Center;
7602  m.Translation += 0.5f * m.Right * Definition.DeadBodyShape.RelativeShapeTranslation.X;
7603  m.Translation += 0.5f * m.Up * Definition.DeadBodyShape.RelativeShapeTranslation.Y;
7604  m.Translation += 0.5f * m.Forward * Definition.DeadBodyShape.RelativeShapeTranslation.Z;
7605  return m;
7606  }
7607  else
7608  {
7609  float scale = 0.75f;
7610  Matrix m = WorldMatrix;
7611  m.Forward *= scale;
7612  m.Up *= Definition.CharacterCollisionHeight * scale;
7613  m.Right *= scale;
7614  m.Translation = PositionComp.WorldAABB.Center;
7615  return m;
7616  }
7617  }
7618  }

8022 
8023  private class MyCharacterPosition : MyPositionComponent
8024  {
8025  private const int CHECK_FREQUENCY = 20;
8026  private int m_checkOutOfWorldCounter = 0;
8027 
8028  protected override void OnWorldPositionChanged(object source, bool updateChildren)
8029  {
8030  ClampToWorld();
8031  base.OnWorldPositionChanged(source, updateChildren);
8032  }
8033 
8034  private void ClampToWorld()
8035  {
8036  if (MySession.Static.WorldBoundaries.HasValue)
8037  {
8038  m_checkOutOfWorldCounter++;
8039  if (m_checkOutOfWorldCounter > CHECK_FREQUENCY)
8040  {
8041  var pos = GetPosition();
8042  var min = MySession.Static.WorldBoundaries.Value.Min;
8043  var max = MySession.Static.WorldBoundaries.Value.Max;
8044  var vMinTen = pos - Vector3.One * 10;
8045  var vPlusTen = pos + Vector3.One * 10;
8046  if (!(vMinTen.X < min.X || vMinTen.Y < min.Y || vMinTen.Z < min.Z || vPlusTen.X > max.X || vPlusTen.Y > max.Y || vPlusTen.Z > max.Z))
8047  {
8048  m_checkOutOfWorldCounter = 0;
8049  return;
8050  }
8051  var velocity = Container.Entity.Physics.LinearVelocity;
8052  bool clamp = false;
8053  if (pos.X < min.X || pos.X > max.X)
8054  {
8055  clamp = true;
8056  velocity.X = 0;
8057  }
8058  if (pos.Y < min.Y || pos.Y > max.Y)
8059  {
8060  clamp = true;
8061  velocity.Y = 0;
8062  }
8063  if (pos.Z < min.Z || pos.Z > max.Z)
8064  {
8065  clamp = true;
8066  velocity.Z = 0;
8067  }
8068  if (clamp)
8069  {
8070  m_checkOutOfWorldCounter = 0; //set position will send us to this function again so dont check twice
8071  SetPosition(Vector3.Clamp(pos, min, max));
8072  Container.Entity.Physics.LinearVelocity = velocity;
8073  }
8074  m_checkOutOfWorldCounter = CHECK_FREQUENCY; //recheck next frame
8075  }
8076  }
8077  }
8078  }
8079 
8080  public static void Preload()
8081  {
8082  var animations = MyDefinitionManager.Static.GetAnimationDefinitions();
8083  foreach (MyAnimationDefinition animation in animations)
8084  {
8085  string model = animation.AnimationModel;
8086  if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(model))
8087  {
8088  MyModels.GetModelOnlyAnimationData(model);
8089  }
8090  }
8091 
8092  if (MyModelImporter.LINEAR_KEYFRAME_REDUCTION_STATS)
8093  {
8094  var stats = MyModelImporter.ReductionStats;
8095 
8096  List<float> improvements = new List<float>();
8097  foreach (var animation in stats)
8098  {
8099  foreach (var bone in animation.Value)
8100  {
8101  improvements.Add(bone.OptimizedKeys / (float)bone.OriginalKeys);
8102  }
8103  }
8104 
8105  float overallReduction = improvements.Average();
8106  }
8107 
8108  // Call moved to MyCharacterSoundComponent.Init()
8109  //MyCharacterSoundComponent.Preload();
8110  }

8397  public bool ResponsibleForUpdate(MyNetworkClient player)
8398  {
8399  if (Sync.Players == null)
8400  return false;
8401 
8402  var controllingPlayer = Sync.Players.GetControllingPlayer(this);
8403  if (controllingPlayer == null)
8404  {
8405  if (CurrentRemoteControl != null)
8406  {
8407  controllingPlayer = Sync.Players.GetControllingPlayer(CurrentRemoteControl as MyEntity);
8408  }
8409  }
8410 
8411  if (controllingPlayer == null)
8412  {
8413  return player.IsGameServer();
8414  }
8415  else
8416  {
8417  return controllingPlayer.Client == player;
8418  }
8419  }

8516 
8517  [Event, Reliable, Server]
8518  private void SwitchToWeaponMessage(SerializableDefinitionId? weapon, uint? inventoryItemId)
8519  {
8520  if (CanSwitchToWeapon(weapon) == false)
8521  {
8522  return;
8523  }
8524 
8525  if (inventoryItemId != null)
8526  {
8527  var inventory = this.GetInventory();
8528  if (inventory != null)
8529  {
8530  var item = inventory.GetItemByID(inventoryItemId.Value);
8531  if (item.HasValue)
8532  {
8533  var itemId = MyDefinitionManager.Static.ItemIdFromWeaponId(weapon.Value);
8534  if (itemId.HasValue && item.Value.Content.GetObjectId() == itemId.Value)
8535  {
8536  long weaponEntityId = MyEntityIdentifier.AllocateId();
8537  SwitchToWeaponSuccess(weapon, inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
8538  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.OnSwitchToWeaponSuccess, weapon, inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
8539  }
8540  }
8541  }
8542  }
8543  else if (weapon != null)
8544  {
8545  long weaponEntityId = MyEntityIdentifier.AllocateId();
8546  SwitchToWeaponSuccess(weapon, inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
8547  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.OnSwitchToWeaponSuccess, weapon, inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
8548  }
8549  else
8550  {
8551  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.UnequipWeapon);
8552  }
8553  }
8554 
8555  [Event, Reliable, Broadcast]
8556  private void OnSwitchToWeaponSuccess(SerializableDefinitionId? weapon, uint? inventoryItemId, long weaponEntityId)
8557  {
8558  SwitchToWeaponSuccess(weapon, inventoryItemId, weaponEntityId);
8559  }

8566  [Event, Reliable, Server]
8567  private void OnPlayerMessageRequest(string text, ulong senderSteamId, ulong receiverSteamId, long timestamp)
8568  {
8569  //Ignore messages that have improper lengths
8570  if (text.Length == 0 || text.Length > MyChatConstants.MAX_CHAT_STRING_LENGTH)
8571  {
8572  return;
8573  }
8574 
8575  var receiverId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerIdentity(new MyPlayer.PlayerId(receiverSteamId));
8576  var senderId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerIdentity(new MyPlayer.PlayerId(senderSteamId));
8577 
8578  //TODO(AF) Check if message was already received
8579 
8580  if (receiverId != null && receiverId.Character != null && senderId != null && senderId.Character != null && MyAntennaSystem.Static.CheckConnection(senderId, receiverId))
8581  {
8582  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.OnPlayerMessageSuccess, text, senderSteamId, receiverSteamId, timestamp, new EndpointId(senderSteamId));
8583  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.OnPlayerMessageSuccess, text, senderSteamId, receiverSteamId, timestamp, new EndpointId(receiverSteamId));
8584 
8585  //Save chat history on server for non-server players
8586  if (receiverId.Character != MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
8587  {
8588  MyChatSystem.AddPlayerChatItem(receiverId.IdentityId, senderId.IdentityId, new MyPlayerChatItem(text, senderId.IdentityId, timestamp, true));
8589  }
8590  if (senderId.Character != MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
8591  {
8592  MyChatSystem.AddPlayerChatItem(senderId.IdentityId, receiverId.IdentityId, new MyPlayerChatItem(text, senderId.IdentityId, timestamp, true));
8593  }
8594  }
8595  }

8597  [Event, Reliable, Client]
8598  private void OnPlayerMessageSuccess(string text, ulong senderSteamId, ulong receiverSteamId, long timestamp)
8599  {
8600  var receiverId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerIdentity(new MyPlayer.PlayerId(receiverSteamId));
8601  var senderId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerIdentity(new MyPlayer.PlayerId(senderSteamId));
8602 
8603  if (receiverId != null && receiverId.Character != null && senderId != null && senderId.Character != null)
8604  {
8605  if (receiverId.Character == MySession.Static.LocalCharacter && receiverId.Character != senderId.Character)
8606  {
8607  MyChatSystem.AddPlayerChatItem(receiverId.IdentityId, senderId.IdentityId, new MyPlayerChatItem(text, senderId.IdentityId, timestamp, true));
8608  MySession.Static.ChatSystem.OnNewPlayerMessage(senderId.IdentityId, senderId.IdentityId);
8609 
8610  MySession.Static.Gpss.ScanText(text, MyTexts.GetString(MySpaceTexts.TerminalTab_GPS_NewFromPrivateComms));
8611  }
8612  else
8613  {
8614  MyChatSystem.SetPlayerChatItemSent(senderId.IdentityId, receiverId.IdentityId, text, new TimeSpan(timestamp), true);
8615  MySession.Static.ChatSystem.OnNewPlayerMessage(receiverId.IdentityId, senderId.IdentityId);
8616  }
8617  }

8681  static private MyFactionChatItem FindFactionChatItem(long playerId, long factionId1, long factionId2, TimeSpan timestamp, string text)
8682  {
8683  var factionChat = MyChatSystem.FindFactionChatHistory(factionId1, factionId2);
8684  if (factionChat != null)
8685  {
8686  foreach (var factionChatItem in factionChat.Chat)
8687  {
8688  if (factionChatItem.Timestamp == timestamp && factionChatItem.Text == text)
8689  {
8690  return factionChatItem;
8691  }
8692  }
8693  }
8694 
8695  return null;
8696  }

8698  static private void SendConfirmMessageToFaction(long factionId, Dictionary<long, bool> PlayersToSendTo, long factionId1, long factionId2, long originalSenderId, long timestampTicks, long receiverId, string text)
8699  {
8700  var receiverFaction = MySession.Static.Factions.TryGetFactionById(factionId);
8701  foreach (var member in receiverFaction.Members)
8702  {
8703  MyPlayer.PlayerId playerId;
8704  bool sendToMember = false;
8705  if (PlayersToSendTo.TryGetValue(member.Key, out sendToMember))
8706  {
8707  if (MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerId(member.Value.PlayerId, out playerId) && sendToMember)
8708  {
8709  MyMultiplayer.RaiseStaticEvent(x => OnConfirmFactionMessageSuccess, factionId1, factionId2, originalSenderId, timestampTicks, receiverId, text, new EndpointId(playerId.SteamId));
8710 
8711  //Save chat history on server for non-server players
8712  if (member.Value.PlayerId != MySession.Static.LocalPlayerId)
8713  {
8714  ConfirmMessage(factionId1, factionId2, originalSenderId, timestampTicks, receiverId, text, member.Value.PlayerId);
8715  }
8716  }
8717  }
8718  }
8719  }
8720 
8721  [Event, Reliable, Server]
8722  static private void OnFactionMessageRequest(long factionId1, long factionId2, MyObjectBuilder_FactionChatItem chatItemBuilder)
8723  {
8724  //Ignore messages that have improper lengths
8725  if (chatItemBuilder.Text.Length == 0 || chatItemBuilder.Text.Length > MyChatConstants.MAX_CHAT_STRING_LENGTH)
8726  {
8727  return;
8728  }
8729 
8730  long currentSenderId = MyEntityIdentifier.ConstructId(MyEntityIdentifier.ID_OBJECT_TYPE.IDENTITY, chatItemBuilder.IdentityIdUniqueNumber);
8731  var senderId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetIdentity(currentSenderId);
8732 
8733  var chatItem = new MyFactionChatItem();
8734  chatItem.Init(chatItemBuilder);
8735 
8736  //Find all members that can receive this messages
8737  m_tempValidIds.Clear();
8738  for (int i = 0; i < chatItemBuilder.PlayersToSendToUniqueNumber.Count; i++)
8739  {
8740  if (!chatItemBuilder.IsAlreadySentTo[i])
8741  {
8742  long receiverIdentityId = MyEntityIdentifier.ConstructId(MyEntityIdentifier.ID_OBJECT_TYPE.IDENTITY, chatItemBuilder.PlayersToSendToUniqueNumber[i]);
8743  var receiverId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetIdentity(receiverIdentityId);
8744  if (Sync.Players.IdentityIsNpc(receiverIdentityId) == false && receiverId != null && receiverId.Character != null && MyAntennaSystem.Static.CheckConnection(senderId, receiverId))
8745  {
8746  m_tempValidIds.Add(receiverIdentityId);
8747  }
8748  }
8749  }
8750 
8751  //Set their sent flag to true, so that everyone knows they already got it (no need for confirm message)
8752  foreach (var id in m_tempValidIds)
8753  {
8754  chatItem.PlayersToSendTo[id] = true;
8755  }
8756 
8757  //Save the flags back in the message
8758  chatItemBuilder = chatItem.GetObjectBuilder();
8759 
8760  //Send success message back to all recepient members
8761  foreach (var id in m_tempValidIds)
8762  {
8763  MyPlayer.PlayerId receiverPlayerId;
8764  MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerId(id, out receiverPlayerId);
8765  ulong steamId = receiverPlayerId.SteamId;
8766 
8767  MyMultiplayer.RaiseStaticEvent(x => OnFactionMessageSuccess, factionId1, factionId2, chatItemBuilder, new EndpointId(steamId));
8768  }
8769 
8770  //Save chat history on server for non-server players
8771  if (senderId.Character != MySession.Static.LocalCharacter)
8772  {
8773  MyChatSystem.AddFactionChatItem(senderId.IdentityId, factionId1, factionId2, chatItem);
8774  }
8775  }
8776 
8777  [Event, Reliable, Client]
8778  static private void OnFactionMessageSuccess(long factionId1, long factionId2, MyObjectBuilder_FactionChatItem chatItemBuilder)
8779  {
8780  long senderIdentityId = MyEntityIdentifier.ConstructId(MyEntityIdentifier.ID_OBJECT_TYPE.IDENTITY, chatItemBuilder.IdentityIdUniqueNumber);
8781 
8782  var factionChatItem = new MyFactionChatItem();
8783  factionChatItem.Init(chatItemBuilder);
8784  if (!(Sync.IsServer && senderIdentityId != MySession.Static.LocalPlayerId))
8785  {
8786  MyChatSystem.AddFactionChatItem(MySession.Static.LocalPlayerId, factionId1, factionId2, factionChatItem);
8787  }
8788  if (senderIdentityId != MySession.Static.LocalPlayerId)
8789  {
8790  MySession.Static.Gpss.ScanText(factionChatItem.Text, MyTexts.GetString(MySpaceTexts.TerminalTab_GPS_NewFromFactionComms));
8791  }
8792  MySession.Static.ChatSystem.OnNewFactionMessage(factionId1, factionId2, senderIdentityId, true);
8793  }
8794 
8795  public static bool RetryFactionMessage(long factionId1, long factionId2, MyFactionChatItem chatItem, MyIdentity currentSenderIdentity)
8796  {
8797  Debug.Assert(Sync.IsServer, "Faction message retries should only be done on server");
8798 
8799  if (currentSenderIdentity == null || currentSenderIdentity.Character == null)
8800  {
8801  return false;
8802  }
8803 
8804  m_tempValidIds.Clear();
8805  foreach (var playerToSendTo in chatItem.PlayersToSendTo)
8806  {
8807  if (!playerToSendTo.Value)
8808  {
8809  long receiverIdentityId = playerToSendTo.Key;
8810  if (Sync.Players.IdentityIsNpc(receiverIdentityId))
8811  {
8812  continue;
8813  }
8814  MyIdentity receiverId = MySession.Static.Players.TryGetIdentity(receiverIdentityId);
8815  if (receiverId != null && receiverId.Character != null && MyAntennaSystem.Static.CheckConnection(currentSenderIdentity, receiverId))
8816  {
8817  m_tempValidIds.Add(receiverIdentityId);
8818  }
8819  }
8820  }
8821 
8822  if (m_tempValidIds.Count == 0)
8823  {
8824  return false;
8825  }
8826 
8827  foreach (var id in m_tempValidIds)
8828  {
8829  chatItem.PlayersToSendTo[id] = true;
8830  }
8831 
8832  foreach (var id in m_tempValidIds)
8833  {
8834  MyPlayer.PlayerId receiverPlayerId;
8835  MySession.Static.Players.TryGetPlayerId(id, out receiverPlayerId);
8836  ulong steamId = receiverPlayerId.SteamId;
8837 
8838  MyMultiplayer.RaiseStaticEvent(x => OnFactionMessageSuccess, factionId1, factionId2, chatItem.GetObjectBuilder(), new EndpointId(steamId));
8839  }
8840  foreach (var id in m_tempValidIds)
8841  {
8842  //Send confirmation to members of both factions
8843  SendConfirmMessageToFaction(factionId1, chatItem.PlayersToSendTo, factionId1, factionId2, chatItem.IdentityId, chatItem.Timestamp.Ticks, id, chatItem.Text);
8844  if (factionId1 != factionId2)
8845  {
8846  SendConfirmMessageToFaction(factionId2, chatItem.PlayersToSendTo, factionId1, factionId2, chatItem.IdentityId, chatItem.Timestamp.Ticks, id, chatItem.Text);
8847  }
8848  }
8849 
8850  return true;
8851  }
8852 
8853  [Event, Reliable, Client]
8854  static private void OnConfirmFactionMessageSuccess(long factionId1, long factionId2, long originalSenderId, long timestampTicks, long receiverId, string text)
8855  {
8856  ConfirmMessage(factionId1, factionId2, originalSenderId, timestampTicks, receiverId, text, MySession.Static.LocalPlayerId);
8857  }
8858 
8859  static private void ConfirmMessage(long factionId1, long factionId2, long originalSenderId, long timestampTicks, long receiverId, string text, long localPlayerId)
8860  {
8861  MyChatHistory chatHistory;
8862  if (!MySession.Static.ChatHistory.TryGetValue(localPlayerId, out chatHistory))
8863  {
8864  chatHistory = new MyChatHistory(localPlayerId);
8865  }
8866 
8867  var timestamp = new TimeSpan(timestampTicks);
8868  var chatItem = FindFactionChatItem(localPlayerId, factionId1, factionId2, timestamp, text);
8869  if (chatItem != null)
8870  {
8871  chatItem.PlayersToSendTo[receiverId] = true;
8872  if (!MySandboxGame.IsDedicated)
8873  {
8874  MySession.Static.ChatSystem.OnNewFactionMessage(factionId1, factionId2, originalSenderId, false);
8875  }
8876  }
8877  else
8878  {
8879  Debug.Fail("Could not find faction chat history between faction " + factionId1 + " and " + factionId2);
8880  }
8881  }

8908  public void SendRagdollTransforms(Matrix world, Matrix[] localBodiesTransforms)
8909  {
8910  if (ResponsibleForUpdate(Sync.Clients.LocalClient))
8911  {
8912  Vector3 worldPosition = world.Translation;
8913  int transformsCount = localBodiesTransforms.Length;
8914  Quaternion worldOrientation = Quaternion.CreateFromRotationMatrix(world.GetOrientation());
8915  Vector3[] transformsPositions = new Vector3[transformsCount];
8916  Quaternion[] transformsOrientations = new Quaternion[transformsCount];
8917  for (int i = 0; i < localBodiesTransforms.Length; ++i)
8918  {
8919  transformsPositions[i] = localBodiesTransforms[i].Translation;
8920  transformsOrientations[i] = Quaternion.CreateFromRotationMatrix(localBodiesTransforms[i].GetOrientation());
8921  }
8922  MyMultiplayer.RaiseEvent(this, x => x.OnRagdollTransformsUpdate, transformsCount, transformsPositions, transformsOrientations, worldOrientation, worldPosition);
8923  }
8924  }
8925 
8926  [Event, Reliable, Broadcast]
8927  private void OnRagdollTransformsUpdate(int transformsCount, Vector3[] transformsPositions, Quaternion[] transformsOrientations, Quaternion worldOrientation, Vector3 worldPosition)
8928  {
8929  var ragdollComponent = Components.Get<MyCharacterRagdollComponent>();
8930  if (ragdollComponent == null) return;
8931  if (Physics == null) return;
8932  if (Physics.Ragdoll == null) return;
8933  if (ragdollComponent.RagdollMapper == null) return;
8934  if (!Physics.Ragdoll.InWorld) return;
8935  if (!ragdollComponent.RagdollMapper.IsActive) return;
8936 
8937  Debug.Assert(worldOrientation != null && worldOrientation != Quaternion.Zero, "Received invalid ragdoll orientation from server!");
8938  Debug.Assert(worldPosition != null && worldPosition != Vector3.Zero, "Received invalid ragdoll orientation from server!");
8939  Debug.Assert(transformsOrientations != null && transformsPositions != null, "Received empty ragdoll transformations from server!");
8940  Debug.Assert(transformsPositions.Length == transformsCount && transformsOrientations.Length == transformsCount, "Received ragdoll data count doesn't match!");
8941 
8942  Matrix worldMatrix = Matrix.CreateFromQuaternion(worldOrientation);
8943  worldMatrix.Translation = worldPosition;
8944  Matrix[] transforms = new Matrix[transformsCount];
8945 
8946  for (int i = 0; i < transformsCount; ++i)
8947  {
8948  transforms[i] = Matrix.CreateFromQuaternion(transformsOrientations[i]);
8949  transforms[i].Translation = transformsPositions[i];
8950  }
8951 
8952  ragdollComponent.RagdollMapper.UpdateRigidBodiesTransformsSynced(transformsCount, worldMatrix, transforms);
8953  }

8955  [Event, Reliable, Server, Broadcast]

9006  public Quaternion GetRotation()
9007  {
9008  Quaternion rot;
9009  if (JetpackRunning)
9010  {
9011  var mat = WorldMatrix;
9012  Quaternion.CreateFromRotationMatrix(ref mat, out rot);
9013  }
9014  else rot = Quaternion.CreateFromForwardUp(Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward, Physics.CharacterProxy.Up);
9015  return rot;
9016  }
9017 
9018  public void ApplyRotation(Quaternion rot)
9019  {
9020  var mat = MatrixD.CreateFromQuaternion(rot);
9021  if (JetpackRunning)
9022  {
9023  float rotationHeight = ModelCollision.BoundingBoxSizeHalf.Y;
9024  var physicsPosition = Physics.GetWorldMatrix().Translation;
9025  Vector3D translation = physicsPosition + WorldMatrix.Up * rotationHeight;
9026  mat.Translation = translation - mat.Up * rotationHeight;
9027 
9028  IsRotating = !WorldMatrix.EqualsFast(ref mat);
9029 
9030  WorldMatrix = mat;
9031 
9032  /*mat.Translation = physicsPosition;
9033  PositionComp.SetWorldMatrix(mat, Physics);*/
9034  ClearShapeContactPoints();
9035  }
9036  else
9037  {
9038  Physics.CharacterProxy.Forward = mat.Forward;
9039  Physics.CharacterProxy.Up = mat.Up;
9040  }
9041  }

9043  public override void SerializeControls(BitStream stream)
9044  {
9045  if (!IsDead)
9046  {
9047  stream.WriteBool(true);
9048 
9049  MyCharacterNetState charNetState;

9051  charNetState.Serialize(stream);
9052 
9053  if (VRage.MyCompilationSymbols.EnableNetworkPositionTracking &&
9054  !MoveIndicator.Equals(Vector3.Zero, 0.001f))
9055  VRage.Trace.MyTrace.Send(VRage.Trace.TraceWindow.MPositions, "xxxx " + MoveIndicator);
9056  }
9057  else stream.WriteBool(false);
9058  }

9062  {
9063  var valid = stream.ReadBool();
9064  if (valid)
9065  {
9066  var netState = new MyCharacterNetState(stream); ;
9067  if (!outOfOrder)
9068  {
9069  m_lastNetState = netState;
9070  SetNetState(ref m_lastNetState, false);
9071  }
9072  }
9073  else m_lastNetState.Valid = false;
9074  }
